%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%203%20weeks%20into%20January%20and%20your%20New%20Year's%20resolutions%20might%20be%20starting%20to%20slip.%20Here%20are%206%20tips%20from%20an%20entrepreneur%20to%20make%20lasting%20goals%20in%202024.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mimi%20Ikonn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a115c76979d7371822bbd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMimi%20Ikonn%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20wellness%20brand%20Intelligent%20Change.%20%3Cp%3EIntelligent%20Change%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKeeping%20New%20Year's%20resolutions%20for%20a%20full%2012%20months%20can%20prove%20difficult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEntrepreneur%20Mimi%20Ikonn%20shared%20six%20valuable%20insights%20about%20making%20goals%20with%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20unusual%20tips%20include%20making%20mood%20boards%2C%20sharing%20goals%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20having%20an%20accountability%20buddy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20New%20Year's%20resolutions%20is%20an%20age-old%20tradition%20that%20sees%20people%20around%20the%20world%20sit%20down%20and%20reflect%20on%20their%20big%20goals%20for%20the%20coming%20year%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20abandon%20them%20a%20few%20weeks%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fhealth%2Fmind%2Fnew-years-resolutions-statistics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EForbes%20Health%20survey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%201%2C000%20adults%20in%20the%20US%20found%20that%20the%20average%20New%20Year's%20Resolution%20lasts%20just%203.74%20months%20with%20only%206%25%20of%20respondents%20sticking%20to%20their%20goals%20until%20December.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20series%20of%20dates%20celebrating%20the%20failure%20of%20New%20Year's%20resolutions%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BQuitter's%20Day%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20second%20Friday%20of%20January%20and%20%26quot%3BDitch%20New%20Year's%20Resolutions%20Day%26quot%3B%20on%20January%2017%20suggests%20there's%20a%20gap%20between%20making%20goals%20and%20actually%20turning%20them%20into%20lifelong%20changes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMimi%20Ikonn%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20wellness%20brand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intelligentchange.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIntelligent%20Change%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20social%20media%20influencer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20making%20lasting%20changes%20requires%20a%20holistic%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20unless%20we%20make%20these%20fundamental%20subconscious%20changes%2C%20nothing%20is%20going%20to%20change%20in%20our%20life%20because%20we%20are%20guided%20every%20day%20to%20make%20decisions%20based%20on%20our%20subconscious%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Ikonn%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20literally%20makes%20more%20than%2095%25%20of%20all%20the%20decisions%20we%20make.%20So%20unless%20we%20change%20certain%20habits%20day%20to%20day%20and%20rewire%20the%20way%20the%20brain%20works%2C%20nothing%20is%20going%20to%20change%20in%20our%20lives%20because%20we%20go%20back%20to%20our%20old%20habits.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIkonn%20offered%20six%20valuable%20insights%20about%20keeping%20New%20Year's%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20goals%20should%20encompass%20your%20identity%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIkonn%20said%20that%20Intelligent%20Change%20launched%20tools%20that%20were%20based%20on%20the%20founders'%20personal%20lives%20to%20help%20users%20develop%20goals%20based%20on%20all%20of%20the%20different%20facets%20of%20their%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIkonn%20said%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20%26quot%3Byour%20whole%20life%20as%20a%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20are%20not%20just%20somebody%20who%20works%2C%20you're%20somebody%20who%20has%20relationships%2C%20you're%20somebody%20who%20has%20a%20relationship%20to%20self%2C%20and%20has%20spiritual%20practises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20suggests%20viewing%20goals%20like%20slices%20of%20a%20pie%20or%20even%20an%20umbrella%20and%20slotting%20them%20into%20each%20section%20like%20it's%20a%20different%20facet%20of%20your%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20warned%20against%20making%20too%20many%20goals%20and%20instead%20to%20narrow%20it%20down%20to%20three%20to%20five%20ultimate%20goals%20for%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20reason%20people%20fail%20is%20because%20we%20can%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20over%20ambitious%20about%20our%20capabilities%20and%20we%20set%20out%20too%20many%20goals%20and%20then%20we%20quickly%20disappoint%20ourselves%20and%20the%20moment%20we%20disappoint%20ourselves%2C%20we%20feel%20deflated%20and%20then%20we%20just%20stop%20trying%2C%26quot%3B%20Ikonn%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20goals%20should%20align%20with%20your%20values%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20consider%20when%20setting%20a%20goal%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bwhy%26quot%3B%20factor%20which%20can%20help%20you%20determine%20the%20motivation%20behind%20achieving%20the%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20strong%20'why%2C'%20you%20will%20find%20a%20way%20to%20get%20there%2C%20and%20if%20you%20don't%2C%20most%20likely%20you%20won't%2C%26quot%3B%20Ikonn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20exercise%20that%20can%20help%20you%20determine%20your%20%26quot%3Bwhy%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20creating%20a%20list%20of%20values%20before%20you%20write%20down%20your%20goals%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20create%20the%20values%2C%20when%20you%20create%20the%20goals%2C%20it's%20so%20much%20easier%20to%20see%20if%20your%20goals%20are%20aligned%20with%20your%20values%20and%20then%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20create%20a%20bigger%20vision%20of%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20an%20'accountability%20partner'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20saying%20%26quot%3Bmoving%20in%20silence%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20popular%20sentiment%20meaning%20working%20on%20your%20goals%20in%20private%20is%20more%20rewarding%20because%20you're%20cutting%20out%20external%20judgment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20Ikonn%2C%20this%20isn't%20necessarily%20true%2C%20and%20can%20be%20a%20mistake.%20In%20fact%2C%20sharing%20your%20goals%20with%20others%20is%20actually%20a%20worthwhile%20pursuit%20because%20it%20will%20encourage%20you%20to%20not%20give%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20one%20thing%20that%20people%20miss%20out%20on%20is%20having%20accountability%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20people%20you%20tell%20about%20your%20goals%20and%20dreams%2C%20the%20more%20chances%20you're%20going%20to%20actually%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20accountability%20buddy%20can%20be%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20who%20you%20can%20check%20in%20with%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccountability%20is%20huge%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20forming%20any%20new%20habits%2C%26quot%3B%20Ikonn%20said.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20we%20need%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20support%20from%20our%20community%20and%20it%20can%20make%20a%20world%20of%20a%20difference.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20goals%20on%20social%20media%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20having%20an%20accountability%20buddy%2C%20sharing%20your%20resolutions%20on%20social%20media%20can%20actually%20put%20gentle%20pressure%20on%20you%20to%20achieve%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIkonn%20said%20that%20one%20of%20her%20goals%20in%202024%20was%20to%20do%20more%20public%20speaking%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20share%20this%20on%20social%20media.%20People%20started%20inviting%20her%20to%20more%20events%20and%20giving%20her%20the%20opportunities%20to%20do%20so%20as%20a%20result.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20is%20fascinating%20what%20happens%20once%20you%20put%20it%20out%20there%20into%20the%20world%2C%20whether%20you%20do%20it%20on%20your%20social%20media%2C%20whether%20you%20do%20it%20in%20person%20with%20your%20friends%20in%20your%20community%2C%20where%20people%20will%20hear%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20and%20they%20will%20connect%20you%20with%20the%20right%20person.%20They%20will%20tell%20you%20about%20a%20workout%20program%20or%20maybe%20a%20new%20job%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMood%20boards%20do%20actually%20work%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hashtag%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fnewyearmoodboard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%23newyearmoodboard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20almost%20a%20million%20views%20on%20TikTok%20with%20users%20putting%20together%20aesthetic%20collages%20of%20images%20and%20quotes%20that%20often%20represent%20their%20dream%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20may%20just%20look%20like%20a%20fun%20activity%2C%20Ikonn%20says%20there's%20a%20deeper%20reason%20behind%20why%20it%20can%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20part%20of%20our%20brain%20called%20the%20reticular%20activating%20system%2C%20which%20helps%20us%20filter%20through%20all%20the%20information%20that%20we%20are%20faced%20with%20every%20single%20day%20because%20we're%20overwhelmed%20by%20all%20this%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20you%20focus%20on%20something%20specific%2C%20it%20allows%20your%20brain%20to%20filter%20for%20opportunities%20and%20people%20and%20ways%20to%20get%20to%20those%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20creating%20the%20vision%20board%2C%20you%20actually%20have%20to%20do%20the%20work%20and%20take%20actions%20to%20bring%20the%20dreams%20to%20life%20but%20it's%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20helpful%20to%20visualize%20where%20you're%20going.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeep%20track%20of%20your%20goals%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20created%20your%20list%20of%20goals%2C%20found%20yourself%20an%20accountability%20buddy%2C%20and%20ensured%20that%20it%20aligns%20with%20your%20values%20and%20long-term%20vision%20for%20your%20life.%20Now%2C%20how%20do%20you%20make%20sure%20it%20actually%20sticks%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIkonn%20says%20your%20goals%20have%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%20clear%20and%20actionable%20and%20something%20you%20can%20measure.%26quot%3B%20You%20should%20also%20avoid%20being%20vague.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20instead%20of%20saying%2C%20'Oh%20I%20want%20to%20be%20healthier'%20you%20can%20say%2C%20'I%20want%20to%20start%20running%20three%20times%20a%20week'%20or%20'I'm%20going%20to%20take%20three%20yoga%20classes%20a%20week'%20or%20'I'm%20going%20to%20do%20this%20workout%20program%20on%20an%20app%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20commit%20to%20it%20five%20times%20a%20week.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20is%20breaking%20those%20goals%20down%20into%20actionable%20steps%20to%20schedule%20into%20our%20months%20and%20weeks%20because%20%26quot%3Bthings%20we%20don't%20schedule%20will%20never%20get%20done.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIkonn%20emphasized%20that%20it's%20not%20always%20possible%20to%20do%20something%20everyday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20real%20life%2C%20there%20will%20be%20times%20when%20we%20feel%20unwell%2C%20when%20our%20family%20needs%20us%2C%20when%20work%20needs%20us%20more%20than%20usual%2C%20and%20we'll%20be%20unable%20to%20actually%20keep%20the%20habit%20going.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20we%20can%20always%20pick%20up%20where%20we%20left%20off%20and%20restart%20the%20habit%20at%20any%20point%20in%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-tips-to-make-lasting-goals-in-2024-from-entrepreneur-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705832521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a115d6dcdb354a98570195%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-tips-to-make-lasting-goals-in-2024-from-entrepreneur-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20uncommon%20tips%20to%20keep%20your%20resolutions%20in%202024%20include%20creating%20mood%20boards%20and%20sharing%20goals%20on%20social%20media%2C%20says%20entrepreneur%20Mimi%20Ikonn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbhaimiya%40insider.com%20(Sawdah%20Bhaimiya)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-tips-to-make-lasting-goals-in-2024-from-entrepreneur-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girish%20Karnad%20and%20The%20Mahabharata%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21132432%2F67b1bacb-eeaa-49a8-a168-1a3562f0e74b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20book%20he%20had%20ever%20insisted%20that%20we%20read%20%E2%80%94%20putting%20copies%20in%20our%20hands%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20Mahabharata.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%88%BC%20Raghu%20and%20Radha%20Karnad%2C%20Afterword%2C%20%3Cem%3EThis%20Life%20At%20Play%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201959%2C%20when%20Girish%20Karnad%20was%20about%20to%20leave%20for%20Oxford%20as%20a%20Rhodes%20Scholar%2C%20he%20felt%20compelled%20to%20read%20the%20epics%20and%20the%20Puranas%20before%20his%20departure.%20He%20had%20grown%20up%20watching%20these%20stories%20performed%20by%20lamplight%2C%20by%20Yakshagana%20and%20Company%20Natak%20troupes.%20Now%20he%20reached%20for%20C.%20Rajagopalachari%E2%80%99s%20concise%20but%20complete%20versions%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20is%20the%20decision%20that%20would%20eventually%20lead%20him%20to%20write%20his%20first%20play%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EYayati%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20aspect%20of%20this%20play%20took%20him%20by%20surprise%2C%20as%20Aparna%20Dharwadker%20notes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20it%20was%20a%20play%20and%20not%20a%20cluster%20of%20angst-ridden%20poems%2C%20that%20it%20was%20written%20in%20Kannada%20instead%20of%20English%2C%20and%20that%20it%20used%20an%20episode%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%20as%20its%20narrative%20basis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20choice%20%E2%80%9Cnailed%20me%20to%20my%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karnad%20said.%20It%20set%20him%20on%20a%20path%20of%20drawing%20narratives%20from%20myth%2C%20history%20and%20folklore%2C%20which%20dominated%20his%20playwriting%20for%20the%20next%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20myth%20of%20Yayati%2C%20a%20king%20is%20cursed%20with%20decrepit%20old%20age%2C%20and%20Puru%2C%20his%20youngest%20son%2C%20agrees%20to%20bear%20the%20curse%20on%20his%20behalf.%20In%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThis%20Life%20At%20Play%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Karnad%20recalls%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20excited%20by%20the%20story%20of%20Yayati%2C%20where%20a%20son%20exchanges%20his%20youth%20with%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20old%20age.%20The%20situation%20was%20both%20dramatic%20and%20tragic.%20But%20the%20question%20that%20bothered%20me%20even%20as%20I%20was%20finishing%20the%20story%20was%3A%20If%20the%20son%20had%20been%20married%2C%20what%20would%20the%20wife%20do%3F%20Would%20she%20have%20accepted%20this%20unnatural%20arrangement%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20imaginary%20character%E2%80%99s%20response%20became%20the%20seed%20of%20his%20first%20play%2C%20written%20at%20the%20age%20of%2022%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20scene%20that%20formed%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes%3A%20the%20confrontation%20between%20Yayati%20and%20Chitralekha.%20%E2%80%A6%20As%20I%20thought%20about%20it%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20play%20began%20to%20take%20shape%20around%20this%20climax.%20I%20did%20not%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20was%20writing%20a%20play%E2%80%A6%20It%20was%20as%20if%20a%20spirit%20had%20entered%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Karnad%20was%20a%20young%20man%20facing%20his%20own%20burdensome%20questions%3A%20Would%20he%20return%20to%20India%20when%20he%20was%20done%20at%20Oxford%3F%20What%20were%20his%20responsibilities%2C%20as%20a%20young%20man%2C%20to%20his%20own%20father%2C%20his%20family%2C%20or%20his%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Karnad%20wrote%20the%20play%2C%20he%20could%20relate%20to%20the%20son%2C%20Puru%2C%20and%20the%20weight%20of%20obligation%20he%20feels%20in%20the%20story.%20When%20he%20read%20the%20play%20again%2C%20much%20later%20in%20his%20own%20life%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20identifying%20with%20the%20desperation%20of%20the%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatch%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzvrEPHuVTZo%3Fsi%3DAta_8Q2EA3mEDi7o%5C%22%3EThe%20Structure%20of%20the%20Play%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20lecture%20by%20Karnad%20on%C2%A0%3Cem%3EYayati%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20Sahitya%20Rangabhoomi%20Pratishthan%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20story%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%20also%20made%20an%20impression%20on%20Karnad%20at%20that%20early%20point.%20This%20one%2C%20though%2C%20would%20take%2037%20years%20to%20become%20a%20play%3A%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAgni%20Mattu%20Mal%C3%A9%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Fire%20and%20the%20Rain%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21132709%2F965c8b05-a7a4-451c-aa20-77de271189e6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21132709%2F965c8b05-a7a4-451c-aa20-7