content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21143815%2F30dea377-150b-497d-8ecd-120fb8a7dd49-300x112.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693877%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22364%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnad%20finished%20the%20screenplay%20%E2%80%94%20now%20also%20housed%20with%20his%20papers%20at%20the%20Ashoka%20Archives%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20film%20was%20never%20made.%20However%2C%20we%20can%20imagine%20what%20it%20might%20have%20looked%20like%2C%20based%20on%20S4C%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQKjcoFZmKuA%3Fsi%3Dg4UVlCh-FQ2XK35Q%5C%22%3Eother%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20a%20few%20years%20later%2C%20while%20he%20was%20living%20in%20London%20as%20director%20of%20the%20Nehru%20Centre%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cultural%20institute%20of%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20%E2%80%94%20Karnad%20was%20approached%20by%20the%20BBC%20to%20write%20and%20present%20an%20episode%20for%20the%20series%20%E2%80%9CArt%20That%20Shook%20The%20World%E2%80%9D.%20The%20subject%3A%20the%20Mahabharata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKM%20Chaitanya%20shares%20a%20memory%20about%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20response%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKarnad%20told%20me%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20said%20to%20them%20that%20the%20Mahabharata%20was%20so%20vast%20in%20its%20expanse%20that%20they%20cannot%20put%20it%20alongside%20any%20other%20work%20of%20art%20in%20the%20world.%20I%20told%20them%20they%20might%20have%20to%20make%20a%20new%20series%20called%20%E2%80%98Art%20That%20Created%20The%20World%E2%80%99%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20make%20something%20on%20the%20Mahabharata.%20I%20suggested%20that%20instead%20of%20the%20entire%20Mahabharata%2C%20they%20could%20plan%20an%20episode%20on%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20epic.%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Miller%2C%20who%20produced%20the%20series%2C%20told%20us%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20decided%20the%20series%20should%20not%20be%20solely%20based%20on%20the%20Western%20canon.%20I%E2%80%99d%20been%20very%20influenced%2C%20years%20before%2C%20by%20seeing%20Peter%20Brook%E2%80%99s%20stage%20production%20of%20The%20Mahabharata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20just%20been%20filming%20with%20Brook%20on%20another%20production%20which%20brought%20it%20all%20back%20to%20mind%E2%80%A6%20Girish%20had%20fairly%20recently%20arrived%20in%20London%20and%20had%20been%20in%20the%20newspapers%20so%20we%20contacted%20him.%20I%20recognised%20his%20work%20as%20a%20movie%20star%20of%20course.%20I%20was%20thrilled%20when%20he%20said%20yes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%2C%20directed%20by%20James%20Erskine%2C%20included%20interviews%20with%20Ramachandra%20Gandhi%2C%20Mark%20Tully%20and%20(against%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20he%20later%20said)%20Murali%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20then%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20NDA-1%20government.%20Watch%20a%20selection%20of%20clips%20from%20the%20episode%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC196PinyF6r%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2AaL21SkMx%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20newsletter%20only%20scratches%20the%20surface%20of%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20life-long%20engagement%20with%20the%20epic%20%E2%80%93%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20distil%20the%20substance%20of%20his%20views%20and%20insights.%20Those%20emerge%20in%20his%20plays%20and%20in%20the%20BBC%20Gita%20documentary.%20They%20are%20there%20in%20an%20intimate%20form%2C%20too%2C%C2%A0in%20his%20studious%20notes%20on%20the%20work%20of%20professional%20scholars.%20Even%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20career%2C%20Karnad%20was%20still%20studying%20the%20epic.%20To%20him%2C%20after%20all%2C%20it%20was%20not%20just%20the%20story%20of%20an%20ancient%20or%20mythic%20war.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Mahabharata%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20always%20our%20latest%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%207