0tanning%20beds%20after%20she%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20having%20one%20in%20her%20office.%20The%2043-year-old%20said%20that%20it%20helps%20with%20her%20psoriasis%20condition.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJumping%20in%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bof%20course%26quot%3B%20video%20trend%2C%20Ms%20Kardashian%20gave%20her%20followers%20on%20TikTok%20a%20tour%20of%20her%20Sknn%20by%20Kim%20offices.%20The%20Skims%20founder%20showed%20viewers%20a%20variety%20of%20items%20including%20a%20close-up%20of%20the%20rear%20of%20a%20custom%20mannequin%20made%20with%20her%20dimensions%2C%20a%203D%20model%20of%20her%20brain%20on%20her%20desk%2C%20and%20an%20in-office%20tanning%20bed%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Fkim-kardashian-tanning-beds-b2481869.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20clips%2C%20she%20reclines%20in%20a%20tanning%20bed%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20Kim%20Kardashian%2C%20of%20course%20%2CI%20have%20a%20tanning%20bed%2C%20and%20a%20red%20light%20bed%20%C2%A0in%20my%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%2C%20Kim%20Kardashian%2C%20don't%20try%20to%20normalize%20tanning%20beds%2C%26quot%3B%20Allure%20magazine%20pleaded%20with%20the%20reality%20star%20on%20X%2C%20the%20platform%20previously%20known%20as%20Twitter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20stats%20about%20tanning%20and%20cancer%20are%20terrifying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20TV%20star%20then%20replied%20to%20the%20magazine%20and%20defended%20her%20tanning%20bed%20use.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20have%20psoriasis%20and%20it%20really%20helps%20when%20it's%20bad.%20But%20I%20don't%20use%20it%20too%20often.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20have%20psoriasis%20and%20it%20really%20helps%20when%20it's%20bad.%20But%20I%20don't%20use%20it%20too%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht