ertain%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705828740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7t46bqf8_kim-kardashian_625x300_21_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-have-psoriasis-and-kim-kardashian-defends-use-of-tanning-beds-4903991%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20one%20of%20the%20clips%2C%20she%20reclines%20in%20a%20tanning%20bed%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20Kim%20Kardashian%2C%20of%20course%20%2CI%20have%20a%20tanning%20bed%2C%20and%20a%20red%20light%20bed%20in%20my%20office.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-have-psoriasis-and-kim-kardashian-defends-use-of-tanning-beds-4903991%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-have-psoriasis-and-kim-kardashian-defends-use-of-tanning-beds-4903991%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-have-psoriasis-and-kim-kardashian-defends-use-of-tanning-beds-4903991%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20One%20of%205%20SC%20Judges%20Who%20Passed%20Ayodhya%20Verdict%20to%20Attend%20Ram%20Temple%20Ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F09194806%2F2019_11img09_Nov_2019_PTI11_9_2019_000298B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Ashok%20Bhushan%20is%20the%20only%20one%20among%20the%20five%20judges%20who%20allowed%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20November%202019%20to%20have%20confirmed%20his%20attendance%20for%20the%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%20The%20other%20four%20have%20expressed%20their%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20is%20now%20a%20nominated%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20will%20be%20busy%20on%20the%20day%20in%20charitable%20works%20for%20NGOs%20started%20by%20his%20mother%20in%20Assam%2C%20along%20with%20taking%20stock%20of%20welfare%20projects%20from%20his%20MPLAD%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20will%20be%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20as%20courts%20will%20be%20functioning%20on%20the%20day.%20Justice%20S.A.%20Bobde%2C%20who%20is%20living%20a%20retired%20life%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20has%20not%20informed%20the%20temple%20officials%20about%20his%20participation%20in%20the%20event.%20Justice%20S.%20Abdul%20Nazeer%2C%20who%20is%20serving%20as%20the%20governor%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20expressed%20his%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20because%20of%20prior%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Justice%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(NCLAT)%2C%20has%20said%20that%20he%20will%20be%20going%20to%20Ayodhya%20on%20Sunday%20to%20attend%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20event%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constitutional%20bench%20comprising%20the%20five%20judges%20passed%20an%20unanimous%20judgment%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20temple%20side%20on%20November%209%2C%202019%20where%20it%20said%20that%20although%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20illegal%2C%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20laying%20claim%20to%20the%20disputed%202.77%20acres%20of%20land%20made%20a%20better%20case.%20The%20case%2C%20the%20judges%20said%2C%20was%20based%20on%20evidence%20pertaining%20to%20the%20claim%20of%20ownership%20of%20the%20disputed%20land%2C%20not%20faith%20or%20religion.%20The%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20was%20also%20the%20first%20not%20to%20have%20the%20name%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Justice%20Bhushan%20was%20the%20only%20one%20among%20the%20five%20to%20have%20made%20a%20separate%20116-page%20concurring%20opinion%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20but%20then%20CJI%20Gogoi%20eventually%20managed%20a%20consensus%20and%20added%20Justice%20Bhushan%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20as%20%E2%80%9Caddenda%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20first%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20apex%20court.%20The%20addenda%20examines%20the%20oral%20and%20documentary%20evidence%20presented%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20about%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20site%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20as%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20birthplace.%20However%2C%20the%20bench%20decided%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20site%20to%20the%20Hindu%20site%20not%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20those%20questions%20but%20quoted%20evidence%20regarding%20the%20competing%20claims%20of%20the%20disputed%20land%E2%80%99s%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705828519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F09194806%2F2019_11img09_Nov_2019_PTI11_9_2019_000298B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fonly-one-of-5-sc-judges-who-passed-ayodhya-verdict-to-attend-ram-temple-ceremony%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%2C%20has%20said%20that%20he%20will%20be%20going%20to%20Ayodhya%20on%20Sunday%20to%20attend%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20event%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fonly-one-of-5-sc-judges-who-passed-ayodhya-verdict-to-attend-ram-temple-ceremony%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Gaza%3A%20Netanyahu%20defies%20Biden%20over%20Palestinian%20state%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705828109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2