ngagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Looking%20Into%20Ayodhya's%20Ongoing%20Statue%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21131336%2FGDZuZ9PbMAEBEro.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHardly%20anyone%20in%20the%20country%20is%20unaware%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Mandir%20politics%2C%20but%20very%20few%20people%20know%20that%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20March%202017%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20particularly%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20state%20government%20launched%20an%20ambitious%20project%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20statues.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20several%20contradictions%2C%20the%20politics%20around%20it%20now%20seems%20to%20be%20its%20undoing%20in%20many%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20politics%20reached%20its%20peak%20in%202017-18%20when%2C%20shortly%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20Adityanath%20announced%20that%20a%20huge%20statue%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20be%20erected%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Sarayu%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Navya%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99%20scheme%20for%20tourism%20development.%20Media%20reports%20were%20soon%20flooded%20with%20various%20claims%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20on%20November%2024%2C%202018%2C%20the%20design%20of%20this%20statue%20was%20reportedly%20finalised%20and%20its%20model%20was%20displayed%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20It%20was%20claimed%20that%20this%20251-metre-high%20statue%20including%20pillars%20and%20an%20umbrella%20will%20be%20the%20tallest%20statue%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20even%20taller%20than%20the%20%E2%80%98Statue%20of%20Unity%E2%80%99%20of%20Sardar%20Vallabhai%20Patel%20erected%20near%20the%20Sardar%20Sarovar%20Dam%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20statue%20of%20Gautam%20Buddha%20in%20China.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20a%20grand%20museum%20will%20be%20built%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20statue%20and%20the%20complex%20will%20be%20connected%20to%20various%20tourist%20spots%20for%20ease%20of%20access%20for%20devotees%2C%20visitors%20and%20tourists.%20It%20was%20also%20claimed%20that%20Rs%20250%20crore%20would%20be%20spent%20on%20the%20project%20from%20the%20government%20treasury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20period%20before%20the%20settlement%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi-Babri%20Masjid%20dispute%20in%20court%20and%20it%20was%20widely%20speculated%20that%20the%20Adityanath%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20BJP%20supporters%20who%20were%20anxious%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20Sensing%20this%2C%20many%20sadhus%20and%20mahants%20began%20claiming%20that%20they%20would%20not%20settle%20for%20anything%20less%20than%20the%20BJP%20keeping%20its%20promise%20of%20building%20a%20Ram%20temple%2C%20and%20the%20installation%20of%20this%20idol%20was%20not%20enough.%20However%2C%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20displaying%20how%20serious%20it%20was%20about%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20statue.%20It%20maintained%20this%20%E2%80%98seriousness%E2%80%99%20even%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20settled%20the%20said%20dispute%20on%20November%209%2C%202019.%20Echoing%20him%2C%20his%20supporter%20media%20kept%20claiming%20that%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20tallest%20statue%20will%20be%20completely%20%3Cem%3Eswadeshi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20famous%20Padamshree%20and%20Padam%20Bhushan%20awardee%20sculptor%20Ram%20Sutar%20would%20build%20it%20as%20per%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20had%20earlier%20selected%20land%20in%20Mirpur%20Manjha%20village%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20this%20statue.%20After%20protests%20by%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20said%20village%20and%20objections%20lodged%20by%20the%20technical%20audit%20team%2C%20the%20government%20opted%20for%20land%20in%20Majha%20Barehata%20village.%20However%2C%20this%20decision%20also%20met%20with%20protests%2C%20objections%20and%20allegations.%20With%20the%20acquisition%20of%2085.977%20hectare%20land%20in%20the%20village%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20statue%2C%20it%20was%20feared%20that%20several%20hundred%20Dalit%20and%20backward%20caste%20families%20would%20be%20uprooted.%20An%20appeal%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20high%20court%20on%20their%20behalf.%20A%20three-decade-old%20matter%20of%20Maharishi%20Mahesh%20Yogi%E2%80%99s%20trust%20seizing%20land%20from%20these%20families%20by%20keeping%20them%20in%20the%20dark%20also%20surfaced%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20amidst%20the%20fanfare%20of%20the%20grand%20Ram%20temple%E2%80%99s%20construction%20and%20consecration%2C%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20idol%20has%20been%20put%20on%20the%20back%20burner%20and%20there%20is%20no%20discussion%20about%20it%20anywhere.%20The%20current%20status%20of%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20in%20Manjha%20Barehata%20and%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20affected%20people%20in%20the%20high%20court%20is%20also%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20does%20not%20discuss%20this%20even%20during%20his%20visits%20to%20Ayodhya%20any%20more%2C%20whereas%20at%20one%20time%20his%20government%20used%20to%20regularly%20review%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20statue%20installation%20project.%20If%20someone%20asks%20whether%20it%20has%20now%20been%20accepted%20that%20after%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20grand%20temple%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20tallest%20statue%20of%20Ram%2C%20no%20concerned%20official%20utters%20a%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20small%20statue%20of%20Ram%20was%20unveiled%20by%20Adityanath%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20Research%20Institute%20in%20June%202019%2C%20the%20media%20continues%20humming%20that%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20tallest%20statue%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20be%20placed%20at%20the%20designated%20spot%20after%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20But%20the%20reports%20do%20not%20offer%20a%20basis%20or%20source%20for%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20politics%20of%20statues%20gained%20momentum%20again%20last%20year%20when%20in%20the%20ceremony%20held%20at%20Ramkatha%20Park%20after%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Lata%20Mangeshkar%20Chowk%20at%20Naya%20Ghat%20on%20September%2028%2C%202022%2C%20Adityanath%20announced%20that%20statues%20of%20%E2%80%98saints%2C%20great%20men%20and%20heroes%E2%80%99%20associated%20with%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement%20will%20be%20installed%20at%20all%20the%20intersections%20of%20Ayodhya%20along%20with%20their%20memorials%2C%20and%20intersections%20will%20be%20dedicated%20to%20them.%20He%20described%20Lata%20Mangeshkar%20Chowk%20as%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20this%20announcement%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20appease%20the%20sages%20and%20saints%20of%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%2C%20who%20wanted%20the%20intersection%20of%20Nayaghat%20to%20be%20named%20after%20Jagadguru%20Ramanandacharya%20of%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%20instead%20of%20Mangeshkar.%20Members%20of%20this%20sect%20argued%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%20had%20a%20wide%20influence%20on%20Ayodhya%20and%20they%20had%20warned%20that%20if%20their%20demand%20was%20not%20met%2C%20they%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20Lata%20Chowk%20signboard%20to%20be%20put%20up.%20When%20they%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20chief%20minister%2C%20Adityanath%20assured%20them%20that%20another%20gate%20or%20road%20would%20be%20named%20after%20Ramanandacharya%2C%20the%20top%20promoter%20of%20the%20Vaishnav%20worship%20tradition%20and%20the%20original%20acharya%20of%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20promise%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20fulfilled%2C%20people%20also%20complain%20that%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20definition%20of%20saints%2C%20great%20men%20and%20heroes%20is%20very%20narrow%20and%20prejudiced.%20That%20is%20why%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20%E2%80%98foreign%E2%80%99%20personalities%20in%20his%20list%20of%20great%20men%20such%20as%20a%20figure%20like%20Swami%20Pagaldas%20of%20Ayodhya.%20When%20the%20statue%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%2C%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20could%20become%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20step-motherly%20attitude%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20what%20can%20one%20expect%20about%20any%20other%20personality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statue%20of%20Vajpayee%20was%20to%20be%20installed%20last%20year%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20District%20Panchayat%20complex%2C%20right%20in%20front%20of%20its%20main%20building%2C%20reportedly%20on%20the%20initiative%20of%20the%20newly%20elected%20BJP%20president%20of%20the%20panchayat%2C%20Roli%20Singh.%20The%20objective%20was%20to%20etch%20the%20memory%20in%20stone%20permanently%20by%20celebrating%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20first%20win%20in%20the%20elections.%20But%20this%20enthusiasm%20soon%20cooled%20down%20and%20the%20BJP-dominated%20panchayat%20forgot%20to%20install%20the%20idol.%20For%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20statue%20continued%20to%20endure%20the%20sun%20and%20rain%20under%20the%20open%20sky.%20The%20panchayat%20finally%20took%20pity%20on%20it%20one%20day%20and%20got%20it%20wrapped%20in%20a%20yellow%20plastic%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20projects%20worth%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20are%20being%20implemented%20by%20the%20BJP%20state%20and%20Union%20governments%2C%20the%20district%20panchayat%2C%20which%20is%20also%20controlled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20did%20not%20flinch%20in%20treating%20the%20statue%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20also%20claim%20that%20the%20Panchayat%20Board%20has%20no%20record%20of%20the%20proposal%20passed%20two%20years%20ago%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20this%20statue%2C%20even%20though%20there%20is%20a%20rule%20to%20keep%20all%20the%20passed%20proposals%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20senior%20journalist%2C%20Indu%20Bhushan%20Pandey%2C%20said%20that%20it%20pained%20him%20to%20witness%20such%20a%20treatment%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statue%20and%20he%20was%20reminded%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anubhuti-hindi.org%2Fgeet%2Fa%2Fatal_bihari_vajpayee%2Fdo_anubhutiyan.htm%5C%22%3Epoem%20by%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaces%20are%20exposed%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnDeep%20scars%20too%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20the%20spell%20breaks%20today%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20truth%20gives%20me%20a%20fright%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20sing%20a%20song%20no%20more.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20the%20evil%20eye%20perhaps%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20city%20shattered%20like%20glass%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20crowd%20around%20but%20no%20friend%20to%20find%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20sing%20a%20song%20no%20more.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20moon%20hit%20like%20a%20dagger%20in%20the%20back%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnRahu%20has%20crossed%20the%20line%20too%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20moments%20of%20liberation%2C%20I%20am%20trapped%20yet%20again%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20sing%20a%20song%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20district%20panchayat%20has%20woken%20up%2C%20perhaps%20owing%20to%20its%20guilt%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20will%20construct%20an%20umbrella%20over%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20statue%20and%20stairs%20by%20December%2025%2C%20his%20birth%20anniversary.%20But%20will%20this%20adequately%20answer%20the%20questions%20that%20have%20arisen%20from%20the%20disrespect%20already%20shown%20to%20the%20former%20Bharat%20Ratna%20prime%20minister%20and%20point%20to%20the%20internal%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKrishna%20Pratap%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehind