hile%20the%20official%20note%20did%20not%20specifically%20mention%20if%20Out%20Patient%20Department%20(OPD)%20services%20would%20be%20available%2C%20it%20was%20feared%20that%20outdoor%20patients%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20consult%20specialists%20during%20the%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20memorandum%20issued%20by%20Rajesh%20Kumar%2C%20AIIMS-Delhi's%20administrative%20officer%2C%20yesterday%20had%20referred%20to%20the%20central%20government's%20announcement%20of%20a%20half-day%20for%20government%20employees%20tomorrow.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20notified%20for%20information%20of%20all%20the%20employees%20that%20the%20Institute%20will%20remain%20half%20day%20closed%20till%2014.30%20hrs%20on%2022.01.2024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memorandum%20said.%20It%2C%20however%2C%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20critical%20clinical%20services%26quot%3B%20shall%20remain%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20sparked%20a%20huge%20outcry%2C%20with%20many%20pointing%20out%20that%20patients%20wait%20for%20weeks%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20months%20to%20get%20an%20appointment%20at%20the%20premier%20healthcare%20facility.%20To%20shut%20OPD%20services%20suddenly%20would%20severely%20inconvenience%20them%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20had%20travelled%20from%20outside%20Delhi%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20good%2C%20affordable%20healthcare%20at%20the%20state-run%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20AIIMS-Delhi%20issued%20a%20fresh%20notification%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20OPD%20%26quot%3Bshall%20remain%20open%20to%20attend%20to%20patients%20with%20appointment%20in%20order%20to%20prevent%20any%20inconvenience%20to%20them%20and%20to%20facilitate%20patient%20care%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafdarjung%20Hospital%2C%20another%20key%20healthcare%20facility%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20has%20said%20OPD%20registration%20will%20take%20place%20between%208%20am%20and%2010%20am%20and%20all%20registered%20patients%20will%20be%20attended%20to.%20The%20hospital%20will%2