E2%80%99s%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Woman%20and%20Child%20Development%20attending%20the%20meet%20told%20the%20agency%20that%20her%20party%20had%20waited%20patiently%20for%20a%20long%20time%20for%20the%20lord%20to%20return%20so%20it%20(the%20temple%20consecration)%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20reason%20for%20celebration%20and%20joy%E2%80%9D%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20also%20among%20all%20Indian%20communities%20around%20the%20world.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20WEF%20delegates%2C%20the%20same%20minister%20had%20also%20talked%20glowingly%20of%20her%20visionary%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ctransparent%20approach%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Cwomen-led%20development%E2%80%9D.%20It%20shall%20be%20propelled%20by%20gender%20justice%20and%20gender%20inclusive%20infrastructure%20that%20will%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20looking%20at%20women%20merely%20as%20contributors%20to%20the%20labour%20market%20and%20treat%20them%20as%20potential%20entrepreneurs%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20all%20this%20was%20resonating%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Davos%2C%20an%20important%20report%20has%20surfaced.%20Titled%20%3Cem%3EBeyond%20Basics%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Annual%20Status%20of%20Education%20Report%202024%20(ASER)%2C%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20survey%20that%20has%20for%20two%20decades%20provided%20vital%20information%20regarding%20the%20state%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20primary%20and%20middle%20level%20education.%20Brought%20out%20by%20the%20Pratham%20group%2C%20the%20meticulously%20crafted%20ASER%20reports%20have%20pointed%20out%20gender%20differences%20as%20also%20deficiencies%20in%20basic%20skills%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20school%20children%20at%20the%20primary%20level.%20The%20latest%20report%20shows%20that%20although%2085%25%20children%20are%20enrolled%20now%2C%20more%20than%20half%20the%20primary%20school%20children%20surveyed%20still%20lack%20reading%20skills%20and%20can%20not%20do%20simple%20divisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fmore-that-half-14-18-year-olds-in-rural-india-cannot-do-simple-division-aser-report%5C%22%3EMore%20Than%20Half%2014%E2%80%9318%20Year%20Olds%20in%20Rural%20India%20Cannot%20Do%20Simple%20Division%3A%20ASER%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20report%20has%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20covered%2034%2C%20745%20teenagers%20in%20the%2014-18%20year%20age%20group%20from%2028%20districts%20across%2026%20states.%20It%20found%20that%2025%25%20rural%20kids%20in%20this%20age%20group%20can%20not%20even%20read%20class%20two%20level%20texts%20in%20their%20own%20language.%20It%20also%20revealed%20harsh%20gender%20and%20rural-urban%20divides.%20Girls%E2%80%99%20progress%20had%20slowed%20down%20during%20the%20Covid%20years%20due%20to%20lesser%20access%20to%20electronic%C2%A0%20learning%20tools%20like%20smart%20phones%20and%20laptops.%20Post-Covid%2C%2090%25%20of%20the%20boys%20in%20the%2014-18%20year%20group%20now%20have%20smart%20phones%20and%20are%20on%20social%20media.%20And%20although%20only%209%25%20have%20a%20computer%20at%20home%2C%2085%25%20have%20learnt%20how%20to%20use%20computers%20through%20phones.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompared%20to%20boys%2C%20only%2019.8%25%20girls%20have%20access%20to%20smart%20phones%20and%20only%2030%25%20of%20them%20have%20an%20e-mail%20ID.%20So%20even%20if%20total%20enrolment%20numbers%20may%20have%20not%20gone%20down%2C%20their%20skills%20have%20been%20adversely%20impacted%20by%20the%20gender%20divide.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20doing%20work%20other%20than%20household%20chores%2C%20more%20young%20boys%20work%20outside%20but%20teenage%20girls%20are%20mostly%20put%20to%20work%20within%20homes%20which%20increases%20their%20work%20load%20but%20restricts%20their%20mobility.%20Interestingly%2C%20boys%20outperform%20girls%20in%20financial%20calculation%20tasks%20however%2C%20they%20(76%25)%20still%20do%20better%20than%20boys%20(70.9%25)%20in%20reading%20texts%20in%20native%20languages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20annual%20meetings%20of%20the%20global%20super%20rich%20at%20Davos%20are%20where%20power%20packs%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%2C%20corporate%20and%20media%20circuits%20have%20usually%20been%20giving%20%3Cem%3Egyan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sermons)%20to%20billionaires%20from%20the%20developed%20world%20on%20how%20Indian%20middle%20classes%20are%20flourishing%20and%20how%20the%20rural%20India%20is%20fast%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%98smart%E2%80%99%20consumer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-women-who-fought-for-justice-for-bilkis-bano%5C%22%3EThe%20Women%20Who%20Fought%20for%20Justice%20for%20Bilkis%20Bano%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20home%2C%20the%20mega%20companies%20in%20India%20showcase%20the%20rising%20female%20talent%20as%20part%20of%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20(CSR)%20exercises.%20It%20is%20politically%20sanctioned%20and%20creates%20good%20PR%20and%20photo-ops.%20So%20we%20have%20chosen%20groups%20of%20100%20or%2020%20%E2%80%98Most%20Powerful%20Women%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20on%20cover%20of%20popular%20magazines%20as%20female%20icons%20and%20the%20mega%20bucks%20they%20are%20making%20draws%20long%20and%20sustained%20applause%20in%20shows%20where%20they%20receive%20awards.%20The%20obvious%20cracks%20in%20the%20image%20%E2%80%93%20when%20one%20of%20these%20women%20entrepreneurs%20gets%20arrested%20for%20murdering%20her%20child%20another%20another%2C%20hailed%20as%20a%20path%20blazer%20in%20banking%2C%20faces%20grave%20charges%20of%20mishandling%20bank%20funds%20%E2%80%93%20are%20played%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20face%20it.%20Our%20real%20history%2C%20like%20any%20other%20nation%E2%80%99s%2C%20is%20also%20full%20of%20stories%20of%20brutal%20gender%20discrimination%2C%20honour%20killings%2C%20mob%20violence%20and%20various%20forms%20of%20greed%20and%20graft.%20From%20where%20women%20stand%2C%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20experience%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20of%20being%20banished%20to%20the%20forest%20and%20being%20rehabilitated%20when%20found%20innocent%20years%20later%2C%20appears%20rather%20different.%20The%20images%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20currently%20being%20seen%20around%20are%20selective%20and%20play%20up%20Ram%20as%20a%20baby%20(%3Cem%3Elalla%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20a%20male%20archer%20much%20more%20than%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20husband%20or%20Kaushalya%E2%80%99s%20son.%20With%20such%20mind%20engineering%20through%20images%20backed%20by%20elaborate%20rituals%2C%20the%20inclusive%20Hindu%20religion%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20becoming%C2%A0%20synonymous%20with%20patriarchy%20and%20patriotism%20as%20the%20warp%20and%20weft%20of%20our%20democracy.%20Is%20this%20why%20of%20late%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20regularly%20seeing%20self-appointed%20moral%20vigilantes%20on%20a%20rampage%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20female%20olympic%20medal%20winner%20sat%20in%20protest%20for%20months%20before%20her%20rapist%20was%20brought%20to%20books.%20Another%20woman%20from%20a%20minority%20community%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20two%20decades%20before%20her%20rapists%20were%20put%20behind%20bars%20and%20then%20she%20had%20to%20move%20the%20highest%20court%20when%20they%20were%20released%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20good%20behaviour%E2%80%9D.%20Watching%20these%20stories%20on%20TV%20you%20realise%20suddenly%20how%20na%C3%AFve%20we%20have%20been%20about%20%3Cem%3Enaari%20sashakteekaran%20%3C%2Fem%3E(women%20empowerment).%20We%20can%20no%20longer%20ignore%20photographs%20of%20women%20carrying%20%3Cem%3Ekalash%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20singing%20as%20though%20they%20are%20in%20a%20trance.%20The%20real%20drivers%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20politics%20and%20media%20houses%20are%20steadily%20strengthening%20a%20whole%20male-controlled%20system%20where%20back-room%20deals%2C%20wiretapping%20of%20rival%20politicians%2C%20the%20media%2C%20Bollywood%20and%20sports%20celebrities%20is%20fast%20becoming%20acceptable%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%20most%20of%20us%2C%20who%20were%20educated%20in%20the%20state-subsidised%20government%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20copiously%20using%20the%20free%20libraries%20and%20the%20Central%20Government%20Health%20Scheme%20(CGHS)%20systems%20love%20our%20nation%20and%20continue%20to%20feel%20we%20owe%20it%20a%20huge%20debt.%20We%20can%20not%20but%20take%20note%20of%20our%20young%20that%20the%20ASER%20report%20talks%20of%3A%20being%20taught%20poorly%20in%20cash%20strapped%20schools%2C%20being%20fed%20garbage%20as%20they%20watch%20TV%20mindlessly%20through%20images%20crafted%20by%20some%20cells%20whose%20intellectual%20thresholds%20are%20as%20dubious%20as%20their%20version%20of%20our%20history%20and%20culture.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20dice%20appears%20to%20be%20loaded%20against%20them%20but%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20are%20the%20inevitable%20playthings%20of%20inscrutable%20forces.%20The%20gender-based%20asymmetry%20of%20power%20and%20learning%20has%20been%20challenged%20in%20India%20time%20and%20again.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20accept%20it%20will%20go%20unchallenged%20this%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E