s%20would%20not%20be%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20January%2021%20notification%20issued%20by%20AIIMS%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20officer%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20notified%20for%20information%20of%20all%20the%20employees%20that%20the%20institute%20will%20remain%20half-a-day%20closed%20till%2014.30%20hours%20on%2022.02.2024.%E2%80%9D%20The%20official%20attributed%20it%20to%20the%20declaration%20of%20%E2%80%9Chalf%20holiday%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20as%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Lalla%20Pran%20Pratistha%20at%20Ayodhya%20will%20be%20celebrated%20across%20India%E2%80%9D.%20The%20notification%20said%20the%20emergency%20and%20critical%20care%20department%20will%20remain%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20other%20Union%20government-run%20hospitals%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20Hospital%2C%20Safdarjung%20Hospital%20and%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Hospital%20%E2%80%93%20had%20issued%20similar%20notifications%2C%20albeit%20with%20some%20riders.%20Their%20notifications%20meant%20that%20OPD%20services%20would%20be%20affected%2C%20though%20partially%3B%20so%20would%20diagnostic%20services.%20All%20planned%20surgeries%20had%20also%20been%20put%20on%20hold%20in%20these%20hospitals.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20revision%20in%20the%20notifications%20of%20these%20hospitals%20till%20the%20time%20of%20updating%20this%20article%2C%20at%2012%3A20%20pm%20on%20January%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21074451%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-7.43.58.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21074451%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-7.43.58.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21074451%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-7.43.58-300x93.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21074451%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-7.43.58-1024x317.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693809%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22371%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENotifications%20issued%20by%20top%20Delhi%20hospitals%2C%20Lady%20Hardinge%2C%20RML%2C%20Safdarjung%20and%20AIIMS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20did%20a%20back-of-the-envelope%20calculation%20of%20how%20many%20patients%20would%20be%20affected%20assuming%20hospitals%20assuming%20the%20hospitals%20offer%20these%20services%20at%20least%20in%20320%20days%20a%20year%2C%20minus%20the%20weekends%20and%20gazetted%20holidays.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20more%20than%2032%2C000%20people%20would%20miss%20their%20OPD%20appointments%20on%20Monday%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20Safdarjung%20Hospital%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20Hospital%20and%20Lady%20Hardinge%20hospital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16522386%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16522386%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16522386%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98January%2022%20a%20pious%20day%E2%80%99%3A%20IMA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20president%20said%20the%20organisation%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0neither%20supports%20nor%20opposes%20this%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20we%20say%E2%80%A6It%E2%80%99s%20a%20government%20policy%E2%80%A6It%20is%20a%20very%20pious%20day.%20Whole%20country%20is%20happy%20that%20Ram%20Mandir%20has%20been%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20IMA%20national%20president%20%3Cspan%3ESharad%20Aggarwal%20%3C%2Fspan%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20January%2021%20in%20response%20to%20its%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20people%20will%20suffer%20much.%20I%20pray%20for%20that%2C%20and%20also%20private%20hospital%20services%20can%20be%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%20and%20said%20he%20would%20give%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20to%20the%20government%20for%20this%20decision%20when%20asked%20what%20it%20IMA%20was%20concerned%20about%20patients%E2%80%99%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98No%20civilised%20country%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20cruel%20%5Bfor%20patients%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20AIIMS%20professor%20had%20said%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20as%20the%20person%20was%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20no%20civilised%20country%20this%20can%20be%20allowed%20to%20happen.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20anything%20like%20this%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20professor%20explained%20on%20gazetted%20holidays%20and%20weekends%20these%20services%20are%20not%20scheduled%20itself%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20so%20patients%20don%E2%80%99t%20suffer%20sudden%20and%20mass%20cancellations%20like%20it%20has%20happened%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20hospitals%20like%20AIIMS%2C%20people%2C%20who%20come%20from%20far%20flung%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20and%20neighbouring%20ones%20queue%20up%20from%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20for%20registration%2C%20and%20often%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20months%20to%20finally%20get%20an%20appointment%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20hospital%20notification%20said%20all%20services%20will%20remain%20closed%20till%202.30%20pm%20but%20OPD%20registrations%20would%20start%20at%201.30%20pm.%20But%20for%20how%20long%20would%20it%20continue%20and%20how%20many%20appointments%20would%20be%20given%20was%20not%C2%A0%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Vardhman%20Mahavir%20Medical%20College%20associated%20with%20Safdarjung%20hospital%20issued%20a%20clarification%20to%20its%20earlier%20notification%20saying%20OPD%20registration%20will%20happen%20from%208%20am%20to%2010%20am%2C%20instead%20of%20what%20would%20usually%20be%208.30%20am%20to%2011.30%20am.%20A%20similar%20note%20was%20put%20out%20by%20Lady%20Hardinge%20hospital%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurgeries%20to%20take%20a%20hit%20as%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20all%20the%20notifications%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20planned%20surgeries%20for%20Monday%20would%20not%20be%20conducted.%20A%20back%20of%20the%20envelope%20calculation%20had%20suggested%20that%20an%20estimated%201%2C200%20surgeries%20would%20be%20delayed%20in%20three%20major%20hospitals%20of%20Delhi%20that%20are%20run%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%93%20AIIMS%2C%20Safdarjung%20Hospital%20and%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20Hospital.%20While%20in%20AIIMS%20surgeries%20will%20now%20happen%2C%20there%20is%20no%20revision%20in%20notifications%20from%20the%20other%20three%20hospitals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16522399%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16522399%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16522399%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20these%20surgeries%20are%20minor%20while%20others%20are%20major%20and%20complicated%20ones.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fdelhi%2Fwant-a-surgery-at-aiims-wait-could-be-four-years%2Fstory-Ndl1iIL8wFEn4Vm5fNPoBM.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Esuggest%20the%20wait%20time%20for%20these%20surgeries%20can%20range%20from%20as%20many%20as%20two%20to%20four%20years.%20Patients%20dying%2C%20while%20they%20are%20kept%20waiting%20by%20these%20hospitals%20for%20surgeries%20due%20to%20overcrowding%2C%20is%20no%20secret.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20now%20as%20to%20when%20these%20surgeries%2C%20which%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20on%20Monday%2C%20would%20find%20a%20date%20and%20time%20again%20and%20how%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20just%20surgeries%20and%20OPD%20appointments%2C%20even%20lab%20investigations%20are%20going%20to%20suffer.%20Except%20for%20Safdarjung%20Hospital%2C%20which%20said%20lab%20and%20radiological%20services%20would%20be%20available%20till%20the%20truncated%20time%20of%2011.30%20am%2C%20neither%20of%20the%20other%20two%20hospitals%20%E2%80%93Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20hospital%20and%20Lady%20Hardinge%20College%20Hospital%20%E2%80%93%20said%20anything%20of%20this%20sort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20questioning%20the%20amount%20of%20state%20attention%20to%20a%20religious%20function%20versus%20other%20essential%20duties%20of%20the%20state%20has%20drawn%20attention%20from%20some%20in%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fortnight%20ago%2C%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20Tejashwai%20Yadav%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbollywoodwallah.in%2Fif-you-fall-ill-where-will-you-go-temple-or-hospital-tejashwi-yadav-asked-these-questions-regarding-ram-temple%2F%5C%22%3Ewhile%20speaking%20in%20Madhubani%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20fall%20ill%2C%20where%20do%20you%20go%3F%20Temple%20or%20hospital%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20had%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20not%20anti-temple.%20My%20mother%20celebrates%20Chhath%20from%20the%20time%20when%20Modi%20ji%20did%20not%20even%20know%20about%20Chhath.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CLord%20Shri%20Ram%20wanted%20to%20see%20his%20people%20happy.%20He%20said%20that%20people%20get%20happiness%20by%20removing%20poverty%20and%20providing%20employment.%20Improvement%20in%20education%20and%20health%20system%20will%20lead%20to%20all-round%20development%20of%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20BJP%20had%20outraged%20at%20even%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20sick%20needing%20a%20hospital%20and%20given%20it%20a%20communal%20tone.%20Union%20minister%20of%20rural%20development%20and%20panchayati%20raj%2C%20Giriraj%20Singh%20posed%20a%20query%20about%20why%20Yadav%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhaskar.com%2Flocal%2Fbihar%2Fbegusarai%2Fnews%2Fwhy-doesnt-tejashwi-build-a-hospital-in-haj-bhawan-132401883.html%5C%22%3Eis%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20turning%20Haj%20Bhawan%20into%20a%20hospital.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20was%20updated%20after%20AIIMS%20issued%20a%20new%20notification%20saying%20it%20would%20remain%20open%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705819808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21080329%2FUntitled-design-17.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhospitals-january-22-ram-temple-holiday-surgeries-opd%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20president