n%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20intrinsic%20value%20of%20the%20night%20sky%20as%20a%20natural%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20historical%20resource%2C%20the%20International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature%20(IUCN)%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20natural%20darkness%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20nature%20conservation%2C%20ecological%20integrity%20in%20protected%20areas%2C%20and%20the%20well-being%20of%20communities%20in%20healthy%20cities%2C%20said%20Prabhu%20Nath%20Shukla%2C%20deputy%20director%20of%20PTR%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20escalating%20global%20threat%20of%20light%20pollution%20poses%20a%20substantial%20risk%20to%20this%20invaluable%20resource%2C%20he%20stated%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dark%20and%20Quiet%20Skies%20for%20Science%20and%20Society%20Working%20Group%2C%20led%20by%20the%20International%20Astronomical%20Union%2C%20has%20recommended%20the%20establishment%20of%20'Dark%20Sky%20Oases'%20by%20national%20and%20local%20governments%2C%20Mr%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Dark%20Sky%20Place%20certification%20focuses%20on%20lighting%20policy%2C%20dark%20sky-friendly%20retrofits%2C%20outreach%20and%20education%2C%20and%20monitoring%20the%20night%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reserve%20has%20inaugurated%20a%20night%20observatory%20with%20the%20district%20planning%20committee%20(DPC)%20fund%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20area%20near%20Bagholi%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20stargazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20measures%2C%20more%20than%20100%20street%20and%20community%20lights%20in%20Wagholi%2C%20Sillari%2C%20Pipariya%20and%20Khapa%20villages%20of%20the%20Paoni%20UC%20Range%20buffer%20area%20have%20been%20replaced%20with%20lights%20facing%20the%20ground%20to%20mitigate%20light%20pollution%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPench%20Tiger%20Reserve%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20top%20reserves%20housing%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Bengal%2