ow%20PHONE%2C%20and%20only%20AFTER%20that%20Roti%2C%20Kapda%20aur%20Makaan%E2%80%A6!''%20Mr%20Mahindra%20wrote%20while%20sharing%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOh%20no%2C%20no%2C%20no%E2%80%A6.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt's%20true.%20Our%20species%20has%20irreversibly%20mutated..%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt's%20now%20PHONE%2C%20and%20only%20AFTER%20that%20Roti%2C%20Kapda%20aur%20Makaan%E2%80%A6!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F49PmgGOYDV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F49PmgGOYDV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20anand%20mahindra%20(%40anandmahindra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanandmahindra%2Fstatus%2F1748593282366722451%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20children%20today%20are%20exposed%20to%20cell%20phones%20early%20in%20life%20which%20can%20be%20detrimental%20to%20their%20health.%C2%A0In%20a%202020%20survey%20by%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%2C%2060%25%20of%20children%20were%20exposed%20to%20smartphones%20before%20age%205.%C2%A0The%20researchers%20found%20that%20''routine%20and%20frequent%20use%20of%20mobile%20devices%20appear%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20behavioral%20problems%20in%20childhood.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thought-provoking%20post%20resonated%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20media%20users%2C%20who%20confessed%20that%20they%20are%20going%20through%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20addiction.%20Many%20also%20expressed%20concern%20and%20spoke%20about%20the%20negative%20effects%20of%20such%20devices%20on%20children%2C%20calling%20it%20''a%20dangerous%20trend.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20joked%2C%20''Newest%20tech%20trend%3F%20Edible%20smartphones.%20Kids%20have%20a%20great%20taste%20for%20gadgets!''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''This%20is%20natural%20these%20days%20sir%2C%20children%20are%20very%20much%20habitual%20of%20mobile%20phones.''%20A%20third%20said%2C%20''Good%20Lord!%20Not%20long%20before%20kids%20will%20be%20born%20with%20an%20in-built%20antenna%20and%20receiver%20and%20our%20thoughts%20would%20be%20our%20speech!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''Indeed%2C%20the%20shifting%20prioritization%20towards%20technology%20reflects%20the%20profound%20influence%20it%20has%20on%20our%20societal%20dynamics.%20As%20technology%20becomes%20increasingly%20integral%20to%20our%20lives%2C%20it%20reshapes%20traditional%20values%20and%20the%20order%20of%20priorities%2C%20sometimes%20placing%20gadgets%20ahead%20of%20fundamental%20needs.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fifth%20said%2C%20''The%20evolving%20priorities%20where%20phones%20seem%20to%20take%20precedence%20before%20basic%20needs%20like%20food%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20shelter%20are%20indeed%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20changing%20dynamics%20in%20our%20society.%20The%20impact%20of%20technology%20on%20our%20lives%20continues%20to%20reshape%20traditional%20values%20and%20necessities.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sixth%20commented%2C%20''There%20should%20be%20strictly%20no%20phone%20till%20they%20turn%205.%20it's%20difficult%20to%20manage%20but%20can%20be%20done.%20TV%20is%20still%20better%20than%20these%20gadgets.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705818540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6img0vn8_toddler-mistakes-food-for-phone_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fanand-mahindra-shares-thought-provoking-video-of-a-child-confusing-food-for-phone-oh-no-4903234%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20video%2C%20a%20child%20confuses%20his%20food%20for%20a%20smartphone%20and%20holds%20it%20to%20his%20ears%2C%20as%20if%20he%20were%20expecting%20a%20call.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fanand-mahindra-shares-thought-prov