2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park.%20The%20animal%20is%20the%20seventh%20adult%20cheetah%20to%20die%20at%20Kuno.%20As%20a%20veterinary%20wildlife%20specialist%20who%20also%20researches%20on%20cheetah%20health%20and%20conservation%2C%20you%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20brought%20in%20the%2012%20cheetahs%20from%20South%20Africa%20in%20February%202023.%20You%20are%20also%20one%20of%20the%20four%20experts%20listed%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20to%20be%20consulted%20for%20advice%20%E2%80%9Cas%20and%20when%20it%20is%20required%E2%80%9D%20in%20May%202023.%20Were%20you%20informed%20of%20the%20symptoms%20that%20the%20cheetah%20exhibited%2C%20or%20its%20death%2C%20or%20asked%20for%20advice%20on%20this%3F%20If%20not%2C%20when%20did%20you%20receive%20the%20last%20communication%20from%20the%20ground%20team%20in%20India%20about%20the%20cheetahs%E2%80%99%20status%2F%20health%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20was%20not%20contacted%20about%20Shaurya%E2%80%99s%20condition%20at%20any%20time.%20I%20learnt%20about%20his%20death%20via%20the%20online%20news%20reports%20on%20X%20(Twitter).%20I%20have%20not%20received%20any%20direct%20information%20on%20the%20health%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20at%20Kuno%20since%20July%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirect%20communication%20from%20Kuno%20had%20started%20to%20decline%20at%20the%20end%20of%20April%202023%20after%20the%20second%20cheetah%20died.%20The%20last%20information%20I%20received%20directly%20from%20veterinarians%20at%20Kuno%20was%20on%20the%2018th%20of%20July.%20Since%20then%20I%20have%20had%20no%20direct%20contact%20with%20any%20Indian%20officials%20involved%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20said%20that%20you%20have%20not%20received%20any%20communication%20at%20all%20about%20the%20cheetahs%2C%20their%20health%20or%20any%20new%20actions%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20animals%2C%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20since%20July%202023.%20Do%20you%20know%20why%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20male%20cheetah%20Uday%20shortly%20before%20he%20died%20was%20leaked%20to%20the%20press%20in%20April%202023.%20The%20footage%20had%20been%20shared%20with%20me%20earlier%20that%20day%20and%20I%20think%20they%20suspected%20that%20I%20was%20the%20one%20who%20had%20leaked%20it%20to%20the%20press%20%E2%80%93%20I%20certainly%20did%20not.%20When%20more%20cheetahs%20were%20dying%20and%20very%20little%20information%20was%20being%20shared%20with%20me%2C%20I%20started%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20out%20of%20sheer%20frustration%2C%20trying%20to%20persuade%20the%20authorities%20to%20keep%20me%20involved%20so%20that%20I%20could%20help%20prevent%20more%20deaths.%20Unfortunately%20it%20had%20the%20opposite%20effect.%20Gradually%20they%20ostracised%20me%20from%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20330px)%2085vw%2C%20330px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400.jpeg%20399w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdrian%20Tordiffe.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40AdrianTordiffe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20told%20me%20that%20you%20are%20%E2%80%9Cno%20longer%20involved%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20project%20in%20any%20capacity.%20Why%20is%20that%3F%20Did%20you%20get%20any%20official%20intimation%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20saying%20that%20you%20are%20not%20associated%20with%20the%20project%20or%20are%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20panel%20of%20international%20experts%20who%20have%20to%20be%20approached%20for%20advice%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20a%20decision%20you%20have%20taken%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20communication%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20formal%20communication%20with%20me%20regarding%20my%20involvement%20in%20the%20project.%20I%20have%20written%20to%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Project%20Cheetah%20Steering%20Committee%20hoping%20for%20some%20reconciliation.%20He%20did%20not%20even%20acknowledge%20receipt%20of%20my%20letter.%20It%20seemed%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20to%20pursue%20the%20matter%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Etold%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20July%20last%20year%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20was%20%E2%80%9Cavoidable%E2%80%9D.%20Is%20there%20something%20that%20teams%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20or%20the%20administration%20(the%20forest%20department)%20or%20the%20government%2C%20could%20have%20done%20differently%20to%20avoid%20this%3F%20And%20going%20forward%2C%20are%20these%20still%20aspects%20that%20they%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20for%20the%20success%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20three-day%20delay%20between%20the%20death%20of%20a%20male%20cheetah%20on%20the%2011th%20of%20July%20and%20the%20following%20death%20on%20the%2014th%20of%20July%20last%20year.%20The%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20that%20first%20animal%20should%20have%20been%20obvious%20even%20before%20any%20post%20mortem%20was%20completed%20as%20the%20neck%20area%20of%20the%20animal%20was%20covered%20in%20maggot-induced%20wounds.%20Authorities%20there%20still%20believed%20that%20the%20male%20cheetah%20had%20died%20due%20to%20wounds%20inflicted%20on%20him%20by%20one%20of%20the%20females.%20If%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20the%20first%20case%20had%20been%20correctly%20diagnosed%2C%20the%20death%20of%20the%20other%20two%20cheetahs%20that%20died%20in%20the%20days%20following%20could%20perhaps%20have%20been%20prevented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20were%20the%20main%20challenges%20you%20faced%20when%20you%20were%20involved%20with%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20main%20problem%20is%20the%20secrecy%2C%20political%20rivalry%20and%20the%20egos%20of%20the%20people%20involved.%20The%20high-profile%20nature%20of%20the%20project%20has%20created%20a%20situation%20where%20certain%20people%20stand%20to%20gain%20significant%20political%20points%20with%20those%20in%20power.%20Scientists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-cuts-short-term-of-biologist-y-v-jhala-who-brough-cheetahs-to-india%5C%22%3Elike%20Professor%20%5BY.V.%5D%20Jhala%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20myself%20were%20sidelined%20for%20wanting%20to%20speak%20the%20truth.%20This%20was%20always%20going%20to%20be%20a%20challenging%20project%20as%20we%20had%20no%20real%20template%20or%20precedent%20to%20work%20from.%20It%20was%20critical%20that%20accurate%20scientific%20data%20was%20collected%20and%20shared%20in%20an%20open%20and%20transparent%20manner%20with%20all%20involved.%20Unfortunately%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20The%20flow%20of%20information%20is%20now%20tightly%20controlled%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20know%20what%20to%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcheetah-experts-not-in-loop-information-deaths%5C%22%3EInformation%20Blackout%20on%20Cheetahs%E2%80%99%20Health%20and%20Status%20Hurts%20Them%2C%20Some%20Experts%20Say%20Not%20in%20Loop%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eyou%20told%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20was%20avoidable%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20specifically%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20even%20issued%20a%20gag%20order%2C%20ordering%20that%20officials%20linked%20to%20the%20project%20not%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%20How%20important%20do%20you%20think%20transparency%20with%20the%20media%2F%20people%20is%2C%20for%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScience%20cannot%20advance%20in%20a%20society%20where%20information%20is%20controlled%20by%20those%20in%20power.%20If%20scientists%20are%20silenced%2C%20conspiracy%20theories%20are%20allowed%20to%20thrive%20and%20people%20and%20animals%20end%20up%20suffering%20unnecessarily.%20The%20truth%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20face%3B%20authorities%20just%20do%20not%20want%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20all%20the%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20would%20you%20say%20the%20main%20challenges%20to%20introducing%20cheetahs%20in%20India%20are%2C%20now%20that%20you%20have%20visited%20the%20area%20(Kuno%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20where%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20ongoing)%2C%20and%20seen%20and%20experienced%20the%20functioning%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%20first%20hand%3F%20How%20can%20we%20improve%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20Kuno%20is%20a%20very%20suitable%20habitat%20for%20cheetahs.%20There%20were%20some%20challenges%20with%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%20last%20year%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20animals%20will%20adapt%20quickly%20to%20those%20conditions%20in%202024%20and%20we%20should%20not%20see%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20same%20problems.%20What%20we%20need%20is%20for%20the%20animals%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20management%20camps%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20this%20has%20not%20been%20done%20yet.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20is%20that%20management%20decisions%20there%20seem%20to%20be%20based%20on%20politics%20rather%20than%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20told%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Findia%2Fproject-cheetah-africa-kuno-deaths-b2376338.html%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20July%20that%20you%20still%20think%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20%E2%80%9Cone%20possible%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20cheetah%20population%20that%20is%20otherwise%20globally%20on%20the%20decline%E2%80%9D.%20Do%20you%20still%20subscribe%20to%20this%20view%3F%20If%20you%20do%20why%2C%20and%20if%20you%20do%20not%2C%20why%20not%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%20I%20still%20believe%20that%20to%20be%20the%20case.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20opportunities%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20cheetah%20range%20in%20Africa.%20Most%20cheetah%20populations%20in%20unfenced%20reserves%20in%20Africa%20are%20still%20in%20decline%20due%20to%20depletion%20of%20their%20prey%20base%20and%2For%20direct%20persecution.%20These%20factors%20are%20far%20less%20of%20a%20problem%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20looks%20like%20more%20cheetahs%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20to%20India%3A%20India%20has%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fdec%2F05%2Fmore-cheetahs-may-arrive-in-india---this-time-from-kenya-2638851.html%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Easked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20another%20African%20nation%2C%20this%20time%20Kenya%2C%20for%20more%20cheetahs.%20What%20advice%20would%20you%20offer%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20sure%20that%20Kenya%20has%20a%20growing%20population%20of%20cheetahs%20to%20share%20with%20India.%20But%20my%20advice%20would%20be%20to%20import%20the%20animals%20in%20May%2C%20just%20before%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20The%20animals%20can%20then%20remain%20in%20semi-captivity%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20Any%20parasite%20or%20other%20health%20issues%20can%20be%20closely%20monitored%20and%20dealt%20with.%20The%20animals%20should%20then%20be%20released%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20monsoon%20season%20is%20over.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20wise%20to%20carefully%20select%20individuals%20that%20are%20not%20too%20wild%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20be%20easily%20monitored%20by%20the%20monitoring%20teams%20after%20they%20are%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705805999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082711%2FF6DODXJacAA5xsc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexclusive-secrecy-political-rivalry-egos-problems-for-project-cheetah-south-african-expert%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adrian%20Tordiffe%20spoke%20to%20The%20Wire%20about%20why%20he%20has%20said%20at%20least%20two%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20were%20avoidable%2C%20why%20he%20is%20no%20longer%20associated%20with%20the%20project%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexclusive-secrecy-political-rivalry-egos-problems-for-project-cheetah-south-african-expert%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chain%20snatcher%20who%20struck%20only%20on%20Sundays%20gets%204-year%20RI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705805201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107022065%2Cimgsize-9800.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fchain-snatcher-who-struck-only-on-sundays-gets-4year-ri-in-six-cases%2Farticleshow%2F107022066.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22REBECCA%20SAMERVEL%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Information%20Blackout%20on%20Cheetahs'%20Health%20and%20Status%20Hurts%20Them%2C%20Some%20Experts%20Say%20Not%20in%20Loop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17142504%2FScreenshot-2023-09-17-at-2.24.53-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Two%20cheetah%20experts%20who%20were%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20introduction%20of%20African%20cheetahs%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20intercontinental%20cheetah%20translocation%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20loop%20about%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20management%20or%20their%20health%20status%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%2010%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20seven%20adults%20and%20three%20cubs%20%E2%80%93%20have%20died%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%2C%20where%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20ongoing.%20The%20tenth%20death%20%E2%80%93%20of%20Shaurya%2C%20a%20male%20from%20Namibia%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fanother-african-cheetah-dies-10-deaths-so-far-at-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eoccurred%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20January%2016.%20While%20post-mortem%20results%20that%20will%20give%20us%20insight%20into%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20cheetah%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%20its%20enclosure%20are%20still%20awaited%2C%20monitoring%20teams%20on%20the%20ground%20observed%20that%20the%20animal%20showed%20a%20staggering%20gait%20and%20weakness%20before%20it%20died.%20Shaurya%20is%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20cheetahs%20that%20arrived%20from%20Namibia%20in%202022%2C%20and%20with%20which%20Project%20Cheetah%20kicked%20off%20%E2%80%93%20launched%20in%20person%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20his%20birthday%20on%20September%2017%20that%20year.%20Twelve%20more%20adult%20cheetahs%20arrived%20from%20South%20Africa%20in%20February%202023%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20adult%20cheetahs%20to%2020.%20Thirteen%20of%20the%20adult%20cheetahs%20now%20remain%20in%20Kuno.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaurie%20Marker%2C%20a%20Namibia-based%20cheetah%20expert%2C%20and%20Adrian%20Tordiffe%2C%20a%20South%20African%20cheetah%20expert%20currently%20based%20in%20India%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20are%20not%20getting%20information%20about%20the%20animals%20except%20for%20media%20reports.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20implementing%20Project%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20to%20ascertain%20if%20any%20of%20the%20other%20two%20experts%20are%20being%20kept%20in%20the%20loop%20regarding%20cheetah%20releases%20and%20their%20health%20conditions.%20It%20is%20best%20to%20keep%20at%20least%20one%20expert%20in%20the%20loop%20since%20they%20have%20direct%20experience%20working%20with%20African%20cheetahs%2C%20an%20Indian%20veterinary%20officer%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20information%20except%20for%20media%20reports%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaurie%20Marker%2C%20founder%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%2C%20was%20involved%20with%20the%20release%20of%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20cheetahs%20that%20came%20in%20from%20Namibia%20on%20September%2017%20in%202022.%20According%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findias-reintroduction-project-on-course-despite-challenges-says-cheetah-conservation-fund%2Farticleshow%2F103728213.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Marker%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cinstrumental%20in%20drafting%20plans%E2%80%9D%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20cheetah%20introduction%20and%20has%20traveled%20to%20India%20several%20times%20since%202009%20for%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20getting%20information%20except%20for%20media%20reports%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Marker%2C%20in%20an%20email%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMarker%20or%20the%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%20are%20still%20involved%20with%20Project%20Cheetah%20in%20any%20capacity%2C%20and%20whether%20Marker%20was%20consulted%20when%20some%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F4th-cheetah-released-wild-kuno-national-park-tourists-glimpse-9078047%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%20into%20the%20wild%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20this%20year%20despite%20months%20of%20captivity%20after%20they%20were%20restricted%20to%20enclosures%20for%20health%20check%20ups%20following%20a%20series%20of%20deaths%20last%20year%2C%20Marker%20gave%20no%20direct%20answer%3B%20instead%2C%20she%20said%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20project%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20spent%20nearly%20a%20year%20on%20the%20ground%20teaching%20about%20cheetah%20and%20the%20reintroduction.%20We%20hope%20that%20our%20work%20with%20them%20in%20training%20will%20pay%20off%20for%20the%20cheetahs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F27223624%2FUntitled-design-74.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F27223624%2FUntitled-design-74.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F27223624%2FUntitled-design-74-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F27223624%2FUntitled-design-74-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-645937%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESasha%2C%20a%20female%20cheetah%2C%20at%20Kuno%20National%20Park.%20Photo%3A%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Forest%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdrian%20Tordiffe%2C%20a%20veterinary%20wildlife%20specialist%20currently%20based%20in%20India%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20last%20direct%20communication%20that%20he%20obtained%20from%20Indian%20authorities%20about%20the%20animals%20was%20on%20July%2018%2C%20and%20that%20he%20has%20not%20received%20any%20information%20since%20then.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20added%20that%20he%20was%20gradually%20%E2%80%9Costracised%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Project%2C%20possibly%20because%20he%20spoke%20to%20the%20media%20about%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20that%20had%20occurred%20during%20that%20time.%20He%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20information%20about%20the%20death%20of%20the%20seventh%20adult%20cheetah%20on%20January%2016%20either%2C%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20post-mortem%20results%20are%20still%20awaited%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%20four%20days%20after%20the%20cheetah%E2%80%99s%20death.%20Last%20year%2C%20Tordiffe%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20wait%20for%20the%20post-mortem%20results%20and%20not%20sharing%20information%20with%20the%20African%20experts%20had%20caused%20a%20delay%20in%20identifying%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20first%20cheetah%20death%20due%20to%20septicaemia%20(officially%20listed%20as%20a%20natural%20death%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%20by%20Indian%20authorities).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20two%20more%20cheetahs%20died%20in%20a%20similar%20manner%20and%20these%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20possibly%20avoided%20had%20the%20experts%20been%20in%20the%20loop%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20no%20formal%20communication%20with%20me%20regarding%20my%20involvement%20in%20the%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20exclusive%20interview%20dated%20January%2021.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20written%20to%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Project%20Cheetah%20Steering%20Committee%20hoping%20for%20some%20reconciliation.%20He%20did%20not%20even%20acknowledge%20receipt%20of%20my%20letter.%20It%20seemed%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20to%20pursue%20the%20matter%20further.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20main%20problem%20with%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Csecrecy%2C%20political%20rivalry%20and%20the%20egos%20of%20the%20people%20involved%E2%80%9D%2C%20Tordiffe%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3EProject%20Cheetah%3A%20Radio%20Collar%20Infections%20a%20%E2%80%98Cause%20for%20Concern%E2%80%99%2C%20Team%20Expert%20Questions%20Ground%20Support%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolitics%20over%20science%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20high%20profile%20nature%20of%20the%20project%20has%20created%20a%20situation%20where%20certain%20people%20stand%20to%20gain%20significant%20political%20points%20with%20those%20in%20power%E2%80%A6This%20was%20always%20going%20to%20be%20a%20challenging%20project%20as%20we%20had%20no%20real%20template%20or%20precedent%20to%20work%20from.%20It%20was%20critical%20that%20accurate%20scientific%20data%20was%20collected%20and%20shared%20in%20an%20open%20and%20transparent%20manner%20with%20all%20involved.%20Unfortunately%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20The%20flow%20of%20information%20is%20now%20tightly%20controlled%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20know%20what%20to%20believe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Tordiffe%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20%E2%80%9Cis%20that%20management%20decisions%20there%20seem%20to%20be%20based%20on%20politics%20rather%20than%20science%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CScience%20cannot%20advance%20in%20a%20society%20where%20information%20is%20controlled%20by%20those%20in%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20scientists%20are%20silenced%2C%20conspiracy%20theories%20are%20allowed%20to%20thrive%20and%20people%20and%20animals%20end%20up%20suffering%20unnecessarily.%20The%20truth%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20face%2C%20authorities%20just%20do%20not%20want%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20all%20the%20answers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Tordiffe%20(along%20with%20other%20cheetah%20and%20veterinary%20experts%20Vincent%20van%20der%20Merwe%2C%20Andrew%20Fraser%20and%20Mike%20Toft)%20and%20Marker%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20July%20last%20year%20in%20two%20separate%20letters%20regarding%20similar%20issues%3A%20about%20their%20concerns%20in%20being%20kept%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20management%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%20and%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20health.%20In%20their%20letters%2C%20they%20noted%20that%20some%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20have%20been%20prevented%20by%20better%20monitoring%20of%20the%20animals%20and%20more%20appropriate%E2%80%9D%20and%20timely%20%E2%80%9Cveterinary%20care%E2%80%9D%20if%20the%20experts%20were%20informed%20immediately%20rather%20than%20being%20%E2%80%9Cignored%E2%80%9D%20and%20used%20as%20mere%20%E2%80%9Cwindow-dressing%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fhave-serious-concerns-how-cheetah-project-is-managed-we-in-dark-foreign-experts-tell-sc-8872128%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Later%2C%20however%2C%20both%20van%20der%20Merwe%20and%20Fraser%20dissociated%20themselves%20from%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20written%20to%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA)%20for%20details%20about%20whether%20experts%20Tordiffe%20and%20Marker%2C%20or%20the%20two%20others%20listed%20on%20the%20same%20panel%20%E2%80%93%20Fraser%20and%20van%20der%20Merwe%20%E2%80%93%20are%20being%20informed%20about%20the%20cheetahs%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20status%2C%20or%20being%20solicited%20for%20information%20regarding%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20release%20into%20the%20wild%20after%20several%20months%20of%20captivity.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20they%20respond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fkuno-project-cheetah-carrying-capacity%2F%5C%22%3EDid%20India%20Get%20Its%20Math%20Wrong%20About%20How%20Many%20Cheetahs%20Can%20Fit%20In%20Kuno%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20expert%20inputs%20could%20be%20crucial%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20the%20Project%20Cheetah%20Steering%20Committee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1927441%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520members%2520of%2520the%2520said%2520Committee%2520are%2520as%2520follows%253A%26text%3DRajesh%2520Gopal%252C%2520Secretary%2520General%252C%2520Global%2CInstitute%2520of%2520India%252C%2520Dehradu%253A%2520Member%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elisted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20four%20experts%20%E2%80%93%20Marker%2C%20Tordiffe%2C%20Fraser%20and%20van%20der%20Merwe%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20consulted%20for%20advice%20%E2%80%9Cas%20and%20when%20required%E2%80%9D%20because%20Indian%20officials%20and%20veterinarians%20on%20the%20ground%20did%20not%20have%20hands-on%20experience%20on%20African%20cheetah%20health%20and%20management.%20The%20Committee%20has%20not%20officially%20announced%20if%20there%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20the%20panel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20if%20at%20least%20one%20of%20these%20experts%20are%20in%20the%20loop%20regarding%20the%20cheetahs%2C%20Chief%20Veterinary%20Officer%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20N.V.K.%20Ashraf%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Ashraf%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fcheetah-india-conservation-animal-deaths-17061a2256f61e4f2350e7ccde3f735b%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20July%20last%20year%20that%20it%20is%20important%20that%20there%20be%20a%20constant%20line%20of%20communication%20with%20people%20in%20Africa%20who%20have%20expertise%20with%20the%20species%20since%20the%20cheetah%20would%20be%20a%20difficult%20species%20to%20relocate%20and%20grow%20into%20a%20viable%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20that%20they%20are%20in%20contact%20and%20sharing%20information%20%5Bwith%20one%20of%20the%20experts%5D%2C%20at%20least%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashraf%20said.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20ideally%20never%20be%20a%20disconnect%20%5Bbetween%20the%20Indian%20ground%20teams%20and%20the%20experts%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20four%20cheetahs%20have%20been%20released%20back%20into%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20since%20December%202023%2C%20after%20being%20confined%20to%20enclosures%20since%20July%20that%20year.%20So%20many%20months%20of%20captivity%20is%20bad%20for%20the%20animals%2C%20experts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fwildlife-biodiversity%2Fcaptive-for-months-experts-fear-cheetahs-at-kuno-may-face-breeding-issues-93548%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20claimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20this%20could%20have%20%E2%80%9Cbiological%20and%20behavioural%20impacts%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20well%20as%20issues%20with%20breeding.%20Is%20this%20a%20concern%3F%20Close%20monitoring%20could%20be%20key%20here%2C%20Marker%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20email.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20need%20to%20be%20carefully%20monitored%20as%20to%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20hunt%20enough%20as%20they%20get%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20Marker%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20know%20the%20areas%2C%20since%20they%20were%20out%20before%2C%20and%20they%20know%20how%20to%20hunt.%20They%20should%20be%20OK%20%E2%80%93%20if%20they%20are%20monitored%20closely.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Tordiffe%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20that%20the%20cheetahs%20be%20released%20from%20the%20management%20camps%20%E2%80%9Cas%20soon%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20this%20has%20not%20been%20done%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705805033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17142504%2FScreenshot-2023-09-17-at-2.24.53-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcheetah-experts-not-in-loop-information-deaths%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Namibian%20and%20South%20African%20cheetah%20experts%20told%20'The%20Wire'%20that%20they%20are%20not%20getting%20information%20about%20the%20animals%20and%20their%20health%20status%20from%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20and%20know%20about%20developments%20only%20from%20media%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcheetah-experts-not-in-loop-information-deaths%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pay%20Rs%2030k%20for%20dirty%20toilets%3A%20Consumer%20forum%20to%20Indian%20Railways%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705805011000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107022237%2Cimgsize-110964.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fconsumer-forum-directs-indian-railways-to-pay-30k-for-dirty-toilets%2Farticleshow%2F107021962.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20District%20Consumer%20Commission%20has%20directed%20Indian%20Railways%20to%20pay%20Rs%2030%2C000%20as%20compensation%20to%20a%20passenger%20who%20experienced%20physical%20and%20mental%20agony%20due%20to%20dirty%20toilets%20and%20unavailability%20of%20water.%20The%20commission%20stated%20that%20the%20railways%20failed%20to%20provide%20basic%20amenities%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20deficiency%20in%20services.%22%2C%22author%22%3