dn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n-300x175.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n-1024x596.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692049%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20supporters%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20Ayodhya.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FNarendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20bitten%20twice%20shy%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20what%20seems%20to%20overwhelm%20their%20psyche%20now%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20temple%20construction%2C%20which%20has%20drawn%20enormous%20crowds%20from%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20country%20and%20are%20camping%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20the%20town%2C%20literally%20painted%20in%20the%20typically%20Hindu%20saffron%20hue%2C%20with%20conch%20shells%2C%20bhajans%20and%20cries%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%99%20reverberating%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20houses%20have%20already%20been%20pulled%20down%20after%20payment%20of%20compensation%20to%20the%20Muslim%20owners%2C%20who%20perhaps%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20accept%20and%20quit.%20But%20it%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20fear%20is%20lurking%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20Muslim%20families%20who%20are%20still%20living%20there.%20While%20older%20residents%20choose%20to%20maintain%20studied%20silence%2C%20the%20younger%20lot%20seems%20to%20be%20vocal%20in%20expressing%20their%20apprehension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20of%20one%20of%20our%20neighbours%20was%20demolished%20a%20few%20days%20back%20and%20I%20will%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20our%20turn%20comes%20next%20any%20time%3B%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20my%20parents%20and%20I%20will%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20a%2016-year-old%2C%20while%20pointing%20towards%20the%20debris%20of%20a%20house%20close%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20school-going%20girl%20drew%20this%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20attention%20towards%20the%20huge%20contingent%20of%20policemen%20sprawling%20all%20along%20the%20road.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20we%20are%20constantly%20being%20watched%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reluctantly%20remarked.%20An%20elderly%20woman%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20divulge%20her%20name%C2%A0sought%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20told%20not%20to%20entertain%20any%20guest%20from%20outside%2C%20and%20we%20are%20required%20to%20inform%20the%20police%20if%20any%20guest%20comes%20to%20stay%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20well-known%20local%20Muslim%2C%20representing%20a%20socio-religious%20group%20sought%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20administration%20had%20assured%20of%20complete%20safety.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20personally%20conveyed%20the%20apprehensions%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20locality%20through%20a%20formal%20written%20application%20to%20the%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20who%20has%20categorically%20assured%20me%20that%20no%20Muslim%20living%20here%20will%20be%20harassed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohamad%20Azam%20Qadri%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20local%20Sub-Committee%20of%20UP%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20besides%20playing%20an%20active%20role%20as%20leader%20of%20another%20Muslim%20welfare%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccompensation%20is%20being%20duly%20paid%20to%20those%20whose%20properties%20have%20been%20acquired%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%9D.%20Asked%20if%20there%20was%20any%20kind%20of%20discrimination%20in%20the%20payment%20of%20compensation%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20there%20is%20no%20discrimination%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20faith%3B%20but%20the%20compensation%20varies%20between%20owners%20and%20tenants.%20You%20see%20some%20properties%20are%20owned%20and%20others%20rented%2C%20so%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20some%20difference%20on%20that%20basis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQadri%20feels%2C%20%E2%80%9Cif%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20police%20remain%20strict%2C%20vigilant%20and%20unbiased%2C%20then%20we%20have%20nothing%20to%20fear%2C%20but%20considering%20what%20Muslims%20had%20gone%20through%20in%201992%2C%20when%20the%20administration%20refused%20to%20remain%20fair%2C%20there%20is%20palpable%20fear%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-six-year-old%20Meraj%2C%20who%20makes%20%3Cem%3EKharauns%3C%2Fem%3E%20(special%20wooden%20footwear%20worn%20by%20Hindu%20priests)%20also%20lives%20in%20Panjitola%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20locality%20in%20Ayodhya.%20His%20tiny%20little%20home%20cum%20workshop%20also%20falls%20right%20behind%20one%20of%20the%20outer%20fencings%20of%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%2C%20from%20where%20cops%20perched%20on%20tall%20watch%20towers%20keep%20a%20constant%20vigil%20on%20the%20area.%20His%2070-year-old%20mother%20Mehrunissa%20looks%20quite%20worried%20and%20fearful%20about%20the%20men%20in%20khakhi.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20even%20sit%20freely%20outside%20and%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20ny%20minute%3B%20I%20keep%20praying%20to%20Allah%20for%20our%20safety%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20old%20mosque%20on%20the%20main%20road%20in%20the%20locality%20has%20been%20on%20the%20VHP%20target%20and%20several%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20take%20it%20over.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20VHP%20had%20even%20managed%20to%20have%20an%20agreement%20to%20sell%20signed%20by%20a%20masjid%20official%20but%20residents%20of%20this%20area%20raised%20protests%20following%20which%20it%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20managed%20to%20win%20over%20some%20prominent%20Muslims%20in%20the%20area.%20And%20that%20includes%20Iqbal%20Ansari%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Hashim%20Ansari%2C%20who%20fought%20for%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20for%20more%20than%20six%20decades%20before%20he%20died.%20Iqbal%20gained%20prominence%20only%20as%20a%20son%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Coldest%20Muslim%20litigant%20in%20the%20Babri%20case%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20evidently%20he%20appears%20to%20be%20totally%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20sure%20enough%2C%20he%20comes%20in%20handy%20for%20BJP%2C%20VHP%2C%20and%20also%20the%20temple%20trust%20officials%20to%20project%20him%20as%20the%20ultimate%20Muslim%20voice%20from%20Ayodhya.%20He%20is%20often%20seen%20and%20heard%20singing%20paeans%20and%20showering%20praises%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20and%20other%20BJP-VHP%20leaders%2C%20crediting%20them%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20much-awaited%20Ram%20temple.%20But%20surely%2C%20that%20is%20not%20how%20most%20Muslims%20in%20the%20temple%20town%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705800652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20204959%2FEffect-76.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fas-ram-temple-event-inches-closer-fear-lurks-in-the-minds-of-4-lakh-muslims-in-ayodhya-district%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20gun-toting%20policemen%20walking%20down%20the%20streets%20and%20Hindus%20from%20across%20the%20country%20camping%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Muslims%20despite%20being%20assured%20by%20the%20authorities%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fear%2C%20recalling%20the%20horror%20of%201992%20and%20its%20aftermath.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fas-ram-temple-event-inches-closer-fear-lurks-in-the-minds-of-4-lakh-muslims-in-ayodhya-district%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'A%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20Is%20a%20Luxury%20Bharat%20Can%20Do%20Without'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20214440%2Fmodi-no-election.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAlthough%20it%20may%20appear%20closer%20to%20reality%20than%20fiction%20for%20some.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespected%20President%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20Committed%20Bureaucrats%20of%20India%2C%20are%20a%20group%20of%20retired%20and%20serving%20officers.%20Most%20of%20us%20have%20held%20high%20positions%20of%20authority.%20We%20write%20to%20you%20in%20all%20seriousness%20and%20with%20enormous%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20write%20to%20request%20you%20to%20direct%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Bharat%20to%20reconsider%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20holding%20the%20next%20general%20elections%2C%20and%20instead%20explore%20the%20option%20of%20declaring%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadame%20President%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlease%20do%20allow%20us%20to%20state%20our%20well-considered%20and%20thought-out%20reasons%20for%20this%20admittedly%20unusual%20suggestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadame%20President%2C%20you%20are%20well-aware%20that%20every%20single%20survey%20and%20opinion%20poll%2C%20native%20or%20foreign%2C%20genuine%20or%20concocted%2C%20has%20reached%20the%20same%20conclusion%3A%20not%20only%20does%20Shri%20Modi%20remain%20the%20most%20popular%20leader%20in%20Bharat%20(as%20also%20in%20the%20world)%20but%20he%20is%20also%20the%20preferred%20choice%20of%20overwhelming%20numbers%20of%20Indians%20to%20be%20our%20prime%20minister%20as%20long%20he%20can%20or%20wants%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20television%20anchors%20and%20editors%20would%20readily%20concede%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20is%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20In%20fact%2C%20Shri%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20is%20the%20greatest%20election%20strategist%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20known%2C%20has%20already%20predicted%20a%20400-plus%20tally%20for%20the%20BJP.%20We%20do%20not%20pretend%20to%20vouch%20for%20his%20methodology%20or%20his%20resourcefulness%20but%20we%20do%20know%20that%20he%20has%20never%20been%20wrong%20in%20his%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Madame%20President%2C%20we%20ask%3A%20where%20is%20the%20need%20to%20go%20through%20the%20motions%20of%20holding%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20%E2%80%93%20admittedly%20a%20long%2C%20expensive%20and%20disruptive%20exercise%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadame%20President%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlease%20do%20permit%20us%20to%20point%20out%20the%20structural%20and%20institutional%20gains%20inherent%20in%20our%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20if%20there%20were%20no%20elections%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20need%20for%20anyone%20to%20cast%20any%20kind%20of%20doubts%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20or%20cast%20aspersions%20on%20the%20neutrality%20or%20absence%20of%20it%20on%20the%20Honourable%20Commissioners%20with%20offices%20in%20Nirvachan%20Sadan.%20Reputation%20and%20image%20of%20our%20institutions%20are%20equally%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20important%20as%20any%20democratic%20principle%20or%20constitutional%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20if%20there%20were%20no%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20would%20no%20need%20for%20the%20Modi%20sarkar%20to%20overuse%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20or%20Income%20Tax%20agencies%20against%20non-BJP%20leaders%20and%20groups.%20It%20is%20essential%20that%20our%20citizens%20have%20trust%20and%20faith%20in%20such%20agencies%3B%20if%20there%20is%20no%20election%2C%20the%20competent%20authority%20would%20see%20to%20it%20that%20these%20agencies%20go%20after%20genuine%20offenders%20rather%20than%20squandering%20their%20energy%20and%20reputation%20in%20going%20after%20the%20sarkar%E2%80%99s%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20it%20is%20universally%20accepted%20that%20elections%20are%20a%20costly%20business.%20If%20our%20proposal%20is%20accepted%2C%20then%20an%20immediate%20pay-off%20would%20be%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20dependence%20on%20the%20two%20or%20three%20industrialists%2C%20whom%20the%20media%20in%20its%20ignorance%20call%20%E2%80%9Ccrony%20capitalists%E2%80%9D%2C%20will%20get%20dramatically%20reduced.%20Once%20the%20cause%20of%20this%20dependence%20stands%20eliminated%2C%20the%20country%20will%20be%20able%20to%20enjoy%20the%20fruits%20of%20genuine%20and%20honest%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20and%20there%20would%20be%20no%20need%20to%20rig%20every%20single%20economic%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20few%20rich%20men%20from%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20we%20know%20that%20all%20political%20parties%20make%20extensive%20use%20of%20muscle-men%20and%20other%20assorted%20criminals%20at%20the%20election%20time%3B%20the%20bigger%20the%20party%20the%20greater%20its%20reliance%20on%20the%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singhs%20or%20Baba%20Ram%20Rahims%20of%20this%20world.%20We%20are%20absolutely%20convinced%20that%20if%20Shri%20Modi%20is%20assured%20of%20an%20(uncontested)%20prime%20ministerial%20innings%2C%20he%20would%20gladly%20put%20half%20of%20his%20own%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20if%20there%20is%20an%20election%2C%20there%20will%20inevitably%20be%20needless%20allegations%20and%20counter-allegations.%20We%20know%20Shri%20Modi%20to%20have%20the%20most%20tolerant%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eshaant%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20persona%2C%20but%20when%20provoked%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20be%20most%20toxic.%20We%20believe%20the%20onus%20for%20making%20him%20use%20poisonous%20rhetoric%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20eg.%20talking%20of%20%3Cem%3Eshamshan-kabiristan%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20Udaipur%E2%80%99s%20tailor%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98minority%20is%20majority%E2%80%99%20in%20Wayanad%20%E2%80%93%20rests%20entirely%20on%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20who%20quibble%20and%20quibble%20and%20quibble.%20The%20polity%20can%20do%20without%20any%20such%20%E2%80%9Cdemocratic%E2%80%9D%20indulgence%20if%20our%20collective%20life%20is%20to%20be%20spared%20such%20cheap%2C%20shoddy%20and%20communal%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20lastly%2C%20if%20there%20were%20to%20be%20no%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%20Honourable%20Shri%20Modi%20would%20not%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20gimmicks%20like%2011%20days%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfast%E2%80%9D%20before%20the%20grandest%20event%20of%20the%20last%20700%20years%20on%20Monday%20in%20Ayodhya.%20We%20shall%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20because%20Shri%20Modi%20is%20so%20unreservedly%20dedicated%20to%20serve%20the%20masses%20of%20India%20that%20is%20now%20Bharat%2C%20he%20finds%20himself%20having%20to%20reluctantly%20go%20through%20this%20kind%20of%20ostentatious%20religious%20rituals.%20A%20man%20who%20is%20burdened%20with%20micro-managing%20all%20aspects%20of%20our%20national%20life%20should%20not%20be%20burdened%20with%20such%20inconsequential%20chores%20like%20electioneering%2C%20road-shows%2C%20rallies%2C%20just%20to%20consolidate%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20vote%20bank%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadame%20President%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20not%20partisans%20of%20Shri%20Modi.%20We%20are%20not%20Bhakts.%20Most%20of%20us%20have%20given%20the%20best%20years%20of%20our%20lives%20to%20the%20well-being%20and%20prosperity%20of%20this%20nation.%20But%20we%20do%20believe%20that%20we%20live%20in%20uncertain%20times%20and%20it%20is%20vitally%20important%20for%20us%20as%20a%20nation%20to%20get%20our%20priorities%20right.%20An%20electoral%20contest%2C%20whose%20outcome%20is%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%2C%20is%20a%20luxury%20we%20can%20best%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadame%20President%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20pray%20that%20our%20plea%20will%20receive%20the%20serious%20consideration%20that%20it%20deserves.%20May%20you%20be%20able%20to%20spare%20Bharat%20a%20bitter%20and%20divisive%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVande%20Matram%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20sincerely%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommitted%20Bureaucrats%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20irregularly%20contributes%20a%20column%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fatmanirbhar%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20Vishwavguru%20Archives%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20believes%20that%20ridicule%20and%20humour%20are%20central%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705800628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20214440%2Fmodi-no-election.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fa-lok-sabha-election-is-a-luxury-bharat-can-do-without%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20Vishwaguru%20Archives%3A%20The%20following%20communication%2C%20addressed%20to%20the%20Honourable%20President%20of%20India%2C%20reportedly%20landed%20in%20her%20office%20and%20is%20now%20being%20examined%20by%20the%20Competent%20Authority.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fa-lok-sabha-election-is-a-luxury-bharat-can-do-without%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Exhibiting%20Forgiveness%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20An%20Artist%20Comes%20to%20Grips%20With%20His%20Lout%20of%20a%20Father%20in%20a%20Forceful%20Drama%20Free%20of%20Feel-Good%20Fakery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705799913000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fbv_D09JBM3xW_570x570.jpg%3Fw%3D570%26h%3D321%26crop%3D1%22