empted%20to%20balance%20India%E2%80%99s%20unconditional%20condemnation%20of%20Hamas%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20with%20a%20reiteration%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20at%20the%20NAM%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20also%20be%20clear%20that%20terrorism%20and%20hostage-taking%20are%20unacceptable.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20must%20always%20be%20respected%20by%20all%20States.%20It%20is%20also%20imperative%20that%20conflict%20does%20not%20spread%20within%20or%20beyond%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20an%20attack%20from%20Gaza%20into%20southern%20Israel%20which%20killed%20over%201200%20people%20and%20took%20around%20240%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20counterattack%20on%20Gaza%2C%20which%20included%20airstrikes%20and%20ground%20invasion%2C%20more%20than%2024%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%20population%20facing%20chronic%20shortages%20of%20all%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20water%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20medical%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%E2%80%99%20with%20Israel.%20India%20started%20to%20nuance%20its%20position%20about%20a%20week%20later%20following%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20big%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20by%20referring%20to%20its%20principled%20traditional%20support%20for%20Palestine.%20However%2C%20India%20was%20still%20among%20the%20handful%20of%20developing%20countries%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20first%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20on%20the%20conflict%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%