Design%20the%20Perfect%20Sustainable%20Jungle%20Retreat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20fondest%20memories%20you%20have%20of%20your%20grandparents%3F%20For%20Luv%20Shekhawat%2C%20it%20is%20childhood%20birthdays%20celebrated%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Jaipur%20with%20his%20paternal%20grandfather.%20They%20would%20munch%20on%20fruits%20while%20birdsong%20provided%20the%20music%20for%20the%20day.%20%E2%80%9CGood%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Luv%20reminiscing%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20grandfather%20who%20served%20as%20a%20Divisional%20Forest%20Officer%20(DFO)%20certainly%20had%20its%20advantages.%20According%20to%20Luv%2C%20it%20not%20only%20brought%20certain%20perks%20but%20also%20cultivated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332168%2Ftadoba-maharashtra-vacation-sustainable-homestay-by-wildlife-conservation-experts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20growing%20passion%20for%20the%20outdoors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20the%20year%202010%20when%20he%20bought%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20Sariska%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Alwar%2C%20the%20deja%20vu%20was%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20once%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20forest%20is%20where%20I%20always%20belonged.%20It%20was%20in%20my%20destiny%20to%20return.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20the%20rugged%20terrain%20of%20Alwar%20nor%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20proximity%20to%20the%20famous%20(and%20controversial%2C%20as%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see)%20Sariska%20Tiger%20Reserve%20could%20hinder%20Luv%E2%80%99s%20enthusiasm%20to%20bring%20the%20area%20to%20life.%20He%20built%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20nature%20retreat%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20christened%20Utsav%20Camp%2C%20a%20name%20that%20borrows%20from%20Luv%E2%80%99s%20paternal%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESet%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20majestic%20Aravali%20Hills%2C%20the%2035%2C000%20sq%20m%20retreat%20built%20mindfully%20using%20local%20materials%2C%20speaks%20the%20language%20of%20nature.%20By%20integrating%20locally%20available%20acacia%2C%20terracotta%2C%20bamboo%2C%20cane%2C%20sandstone%2C%20and%20rosewood%20into%20its%20decor%20and%20architecture%2C%20Luv%20has%20infused%20a%20unique%20personality%20into%20every%20element%20that%20dots%20this%20lodge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-1705577110.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tigers%20are%20a%20common%20feature%20near%20Utsav%20Camp%20due%20to%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Sariska%20Tiger%20Reserve%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-1705577110.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-1705577110-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-1705577110-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-1705577110-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-1705577110-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338520%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETigers%20are%20a%20common%20feature%20near%20Utsav%20Camp%20due%20to%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Sariska%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Luv%3C%2Ffigcaption%3