Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20ready%20with%20his%20produce%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20it%20at%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20market%20rate%20was%20Rs%20300%20but%20those%20are%20not%20pure%20and%20are%20usually%20chemically%20grown.%20I%20had%20them%20tested%20and%20mine%20produce%20was%20sold%20for%20more%20than%20the%20market%20price%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20gleamingly%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculating%20that%20his%20investment%20will%20soon%20get%20returns%2C%20Gaurav%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20thing%20about%20using%20this%20technique%20is%20that%20it%20does%20not%20require%20me%20to%20follow%20the%20seasons.%20This%20makes%20the%20produce%20available%20to%20you%20throughout%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20technique%20was%20also%20very%20well%20received%20by%20the%20people%20around%20him.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20my%20city%20have%20shown%20interest%20in%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281269%2Fhow-to-grow-potatoes-using-aeroponics-at-home-yield%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20use%20aeroponics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20already%20taught%20it%20to%20five%20people%20and%20I%20get%20inquiries%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelling%20his%20produce%20under%20the%20name%20of%20Shoolini%20Saffron%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20planning%20to%20expand%20the%20production%20more%20and%20reach%20more%20customers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20buy%20the%20saffron%20or%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20aeroponics%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20Gaurav%20at%2098166%2011119.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705416374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-4-1-1705412699.jpg%22%2C%22originID%2